\id 1SA
\toc1 Samuel Khatna
\toc2 1 Samuel
\toc3 1 Samuel
\mt1 SAMUEL
\mt2 LEKHABU KHATNA
\mt3 Samuel Lekhabu Khatna Sung Thu Umdan
\ip Samuel lekhabu tenia hin, tukhang idin mun utoh kitoh in thilphabep aum'inahi. Hatsahna le lungsatna ato hou nasimdoh akon, nangman jong thil tampi nalam doh thei ding—chule hinkhoa hin Pathen beijin ima ahithei poi, ti nahetdoh ding ahi. Chujongleh Pakai, Pathen hi amite chunga akitah jinge, ti Samuel lekhabu khatna hin aphong doh e.
\ip Hiche lekhabu nasim akon hi, Isralete chunga vaihom lamkai chu Pathen mi ham ahilouleh Pathen mi hilou ham ti, nahetdoh ding ahi. Hiche lekhabu hin, Saul lengpa le David, lamkai ahina lhon akibah louna aum'e ti kicheh tah in aseijin ahi. Hinlah anitah lhon’a Pathen thaonu chang ahilhonin, chule thil tampi jong atongdoh lhonin ahi. Chujongleh anitah lhonin alosam kitlhonin, chonset achun alhalut lhon tai. Hiche lamkai teni kah’a akikheh nalhon hi ipi pen ham? Saul chun achonset asel mang kigon, David chun kisih a lunghei ding atin ahi.
\ip Koima achamkim aumpon, ibonchaovin ilhasam sohkeijun, ahin hiche lhahsamna chu hinkhoa thusim achaina ahipoi. David banga lungput dalha’a Pathen henga kile kit ding phajo ham, ahilouleh Saul banga mihem maivea chonset phongdoh louding phajo ham? Hiche teni lah a hi, hoiche pen nalhen ding ham? Hiche ivetkah teniuva kon hi hoiche nalhen’a chule hoiche pen napeldoh ding ham?
\is1 Lekhabu Jihpa Chule Akijih Kum
\ip Koipen in ajih ham ti, akimin phah pon ahi. Hinlah Samuel themgao, Nathan le Gad in hiche thucheng jouse hi anakhol khom uva (1Chro. 29:29), hichu Samuel Khatna le Samuel Nina’a kigom khom ahi.
\ip Hiche lekhabu hi 925 BC vel’a kijih din ginchat ahin, chule solam le lhanglam kihop khen jou 930 BC vel’a ana kijih ahi.
\c 1
\s1 Elkanah Le Ainsung Mite
\p 
\v 1 Masang laiyin Elkanah kiti mikhat Ramah kho thinglhang gam molsang Ramathiam Zophim mun’ah anachengin ahi. Ama chu Jeroham chapa, Elihu chapa, Tohu chapa, Zuph chapa, Ephriam mi ahi.
\v 2 Elkanah in ji ni aneiyin, Hannah le Peninnah ahi. Peninnah in cha aneiyin, ahin Hannah vang'in aneipoi.
\v 3 Elkanah hi kumseh leh Shiloh a Pakai van gam sepaite henga gan kilhaina maicham semdin acheyin ahi.Hiche lai chun Eli Pakai thempu pan chapa ni aneiyin ahi, amani min chu Hopni le Phinehe ahi lhon'e.
\v 4 Elkanah hin gan kilhaina abolni tengleh achan dingdol sachan chu Peninnah le achate apeyin ahi.
\v 5 Chule Hannah angailut jeh chun, Pakaiyin anaobu akhapeh jeh chun, sachan chan khat bou apeyin ahi.
\v 6 Chumale Pakaiyin Hannah chu anaobu akhapeh jeh chun, Peninnah in jong Hannah chu noise tah in alunghan han nadin totnopnan abolyin ahi.
\v 7 Kumlhun seh leh abang bang ahiyingin-Hannah Pakai hou dinga Hou-In'a achetengleh Peninnah kitinu hin phin lunghang jin , hijeh chun amanu akapin anjong aneji tapon ahi.
\v 8 “Ipi jeh a naka ham, Hannah?”
\p Elkanah in adongin,
\p “Ibola an nelouva umah nahim? Chule ibola lungkhama um nahim? Kei neinei hime-chapa somkhat neiho sanga kaphatchom joh louham? ati.
\s1 Hannah Chapa Dia Ataona
\p 
\v 9 ama hon Shiloh’a gan kilhaina anneh, twidon achaiphat’un, Hannah akipatdoh in taodingin achetai. Eli thempu chu Pakai Hou-In khombul khatna touna chunga touva ahi.
\v 10 Hannah vang chu lhase beh seh jengin, Pakai henga atauvin, lhasetah in akapjah in ahi.
\v 11 Chule amanun kitepna khat aneiyin, “O Van gam Sepaite Pakai, gentheiya ka kana neihin velhin lang kataona neihin ngailhah peh inlang ‘chapa khat neipetan,’” ati. \x + \xo 1:11 \xt Minbu 6:5\x*
\v 12 Amanu Pakai henga ataopet’in Eli thempun ane phunchu ana mulhin ahi.
\v 13 Anephu achaloh chu amun, ahinlah ataogin aw chu ajapoi, ageldan in amanu hin ju adonkham hinte ati ahi.
\v 14 Aman Hannah jah a “Hilai munna hi jukham puma nahung ham? Najukham chu paidoh loijin,” ati.
\v 15 “Kahipoi, kapu!” tin adonbut’e, “Keiman ju kadonpoi, chule khamnathei ho jong kadonpoi, ahinlah kei hi numei genthei chungnung kahi, Pakai agsunga hi kahinna pumpia thuseijoh kahi bouve,” ati.
\v 16 “Keima numei phalouvin neigel hihbeh in! Ahinlah lung genthei puma taojing jengjoh kahi bouve,” ati.
\v 17 Hiche chung thu ahin Elin hitin ana seipeh in ahi, “Lungmongin chetan,
\p Israel Pathen'in nathilthum jouse chu nasan peh intin phatthei naboh hen.”
\p 
\v 18 Hannah in jong, “Oh hepu kakipah e!”
\p atin, akinunglen an anepantai, alungkham tapon ahi.
\s1 Samuel Ahungpen Le Akilhandohna
\p 
\v 19 Ajingkah khovah matah in a insung pumpi athouvun, Pakai houkit dingin ache tauve. Chujou’in ain’u Ramah ah ahung kile kit tauvin ahi.
\v 20 Chule Hannah chun aphat chan, naosen pasal khat aneitai. Amanun jong amin Samuel asahtai, ajeh chu “Ama ding’a hi Pakai kom'a kathum ahi,” ati.
\v 21 Akum kit’in Elkanah le a insung mite jouse kum kichaiya gan kilhaina-a Pakai hou dingin akitol kit tauve.
\v 22 Ahinlah Hannah chu anache tapon ahi. Ainneipu kom'ah hitin aseiyin, “Naosen aletdom kahsen ngah hitin kumkit tengleh keiman hinpui ingting, imatih chana dingin Pakai toh umden tante,” ati.
\v 23 Nasei chu aphaselle tin Elkanah in pha asatai. “Tutadin hichea hin uminlang, Pakaiyin nakitepna banginnapanpi hen.” Hijeh chun amanu inah aumin, naosen aletdom kahsen aumpin ahi.
\v 24 Chuin naosen ahunglet domphat in, Hannah in Shiloh a pon-in ah ahinpuiyin ahi. Ama hon bongchal kumthum lhingsa khat toh ahinpui thauvin, changbong neldisel Ephah dimkhat toh apon lengpitwi peng thei khat dimset toh akidop’in naosen chapang chu Shiloh khoa Pakai houna in ah ahin puilut tai, naosen chu chapang chabou ahi nalaiye.
\v 25 Bongchal atha jou phat’un ama hon naosen chu Eli thempu kom ahin puilut tauve.
\v 26 “Kapuu, neigeldoh em?” tin Hannah in adongin ahi. “Keima kum tampi hilai mun'a Pakai henga anatao jing numei nu chu kahi,” ati.
\v 27 “Pakai kom'a hiche chapa hi eipeh dia ana taojing kahin, Pakaiyin kataona eidonbut pen tan ahi,” ati.
\v 28 “Tun keiman ama hi Pakai henga kahin pehdoh ahitai. Ahinkho lhumkeiya dinga kapehdoh ahitai. Hichun ama hon hikom'a chun Pakai chibai aboh tauve.
\c 2
\s1 Hannah Labol
\p 
\v 1 Chuin hiti hin Hannah ataovin, “Kalungsung Pakaiyah akipah jinge, Pakaiyin eihat sah tai, \x + \xo 2:1 \xt Lk 1:46-55\x*
\p Tun kamelma te donbutna ding kanei tai;
\p Kakipahe’ ajeh chu nangman neilhatdoh tai.
\p 
\v 2 Pakai tobanga theng adang aumpoi!
\p Nangma tobang koima dang aumpoi,
\p Eiho Pathen tobang songpi dang aumpoi.
\p 
\v 3 Kiletsah vallin thu seidan, Hoitho nathu
\p Nakam’in phapoh hih hellin.
\p ahetlou imacha aumpoi, natohho jouse thu atan ding ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Galhat te thalpi jouse tunvang akiheh bongtan, mi thalhom chu thahat akisotai.
\v 5 Oi vasetna neten, neh ding nelouvin kel thoh in aum’un, agilkelho avasoh tauve.
\v 6 Pakaiyin thina le hinna ani gellin apen, aman abang lhankhuh ah alhahsuh sah in, abang akaithouve.
\v 7 Pakaiyin abang avaichat sah’in, adang ahao sah in choisang'in. abang alhahsuh sah in abang aphong dingin ahi.
\v 8 Aman vaichaho leivuija kon'in aphong sangin chule angaichate vutvam lah a kon’in aneiloute achoisangin ahi.
\p Leng chapa te lah a tousah ding leh, loupina laltouna-a tousah-a, thilsemho jouse hi Pakai ja ding ahi, chule vannoija thilho jouse kitoh tah in akoiye.
\p 
\v 9 Aman ama dinga tahsan umtah ho chu aventup ding ahi, ahinlah michonse ho chu muthim lah a mangthah ding ahiuve. Ajeh chu athahat na a koimacha dingjoulou ding ahi.
\v 10 Pakai douna-a galsat ho chu cheh chao ding ahiuve, amaho douna-a van'a konna keh alhah sah ding ahi; Pakaiyin van'a kon'in thu ahin tan in ama dinga thaonu changho chung ah, vannoija aman alengho thuneina apen a thaneinau abelap peh in ahi.
\v 11 Chujouvin Samuel jaolouvin, Elkanah jong a in lam Ramah kho ah akiletan ahi.
\s1 Eli Thempu Chapa Phalou Teni
\p 
\v 12 Eli chapa teni chu migilou michavai ahilhon toh kilhon’in Pakai gin na le jana pelou ahi lhon'e.
\v 13 Hichelaiya thempu hija atoh dingdol mi koi tobang hamkhat in kilhaina atodoh teng lhachapa chun, sa kithat kihonsou pet tah leh satul kathum neikhat ahin puma ahinsol jia ahi.
\v 14 Hiche thihkhe chu khangbel sunga asolutna, asodoh pen pen chu Eli chate apeh ding, Israel chate Shiloh a gan kilhaina hunglha jouse hitia chu gihna aneiji lhon ahi.
\v 15 Abang kom le sathaoho kilhutvam masangle thempupa sohpa chu hunga kilhaina ganthatpa jah a chu hitia ahung seijin, “Thempupa kigo ding sahing neipen, ajeh chu aman nangma honminsa chu akilah louhel ding ahi, sahing bou adei ahiye,” tia ahung sei ding ahi.
\v 16 Mihem gan kilhaina kin sempa chun hitin adonbut jin ahi, “Nadeijat jat kilah in, ahinlah athao kihallha masading ahi,” atijin, ahin thempu sohpan jong, “Ahipoi nangman atuma neipeh doh ding ahi, achuti louva ahileh keiman pumhatna kalah Peh ding nahi,” tin aseijin ahi.
\v 17 Hiti chun hiche khangthah teni chonsetna chu akhohlheh jengtan, ajeh chu Pakai maicham jeng jong chu kimit thipna changing aneitauvin ahi.
\v 18 Ahinlah Samuel chu chapang cha hijongleh, Pakai lhachan apangtai. Thempu kivonna tupat ponnem khat in akong akigah jin Pakai angsung'ah lhachan apang jitan ahi.
\v 19 Kumseh leh anun sangkhol chol neo khat akhuipeh in ainneipu toh kilhaina gantha boldingin achekhom lhonin ahi.
\v 20 Inlama ahung kile masang teng’u leh, Eli in Elkanah le ainneipi phatthei abohjin chule hitin aseiji’e, “Pakaiyin hiche na inneipi chapa khat napeh jeh in, amanu’a kon'in chale nao tampi nahinsah hen,” tin aseiye.
\v 21 Chule Pakaiyin chapa thumle chanu ni apen, hiti chun Samuel chu Pakai angsung’a ahung khangtou touvin ahi.
\v 22 Tun Eli chu ateh lheh jeng tan, chujongleh achapa tenin Israel mi tampi abol nalhon thu kithang, kikhopna ponbuh kotpi phunga lhacha a pang numeiho aluppi lhon jong ajatai.
\v 23 Hijeh chun Eli in ajah lhon ah, “Nathilbol lhon jouse Israel mipiten kakom'a aseiyun kajasohkeitai, ipi bolla hitobang chonsetna hi nabol lhon ham?
\v 24 Na ngah teitei lhon ding ahi, kacha teni! Pakai mitea konna kajah thucheng ho hi ahoihihbeh jengin ahi.
\v 25 Mihem khat chu mihem dang khat douna-a achonsetna ahileh Pathen'in asuhcham thei ahi, amavang mihem khat chu Pakai douna a achonsetna ahileh, koipen in ama dinga asei champeh ding hitam?” ati. Ahinlah Eli chapa tenin apa thusei ngainah sah in anei lhon poi. Hijeh chun Pakaiyin amani thina ding gonsan akoitai.
\v 26 Chapang cha hijongleh, Samuel vang chu Pakai le mihemte mitmu’n akhangtou touvin ahi. \x + \xo 2:26 \xt Lk 2:52\x*
\v 27 Nikhat hi Pathen mi khat Eli kom'a ahungin, ahin ama chu Pakaiya kon'in thu ahinpo in, hitin aseipeh tai, “Keima, Egypt gamsung Pharaoh insunga sohchanga aumlaiyuva napa insung mite henga kei le kei kiphong doh’a kahitai.
\v 28 Keiman Aaron hi Israel phung jousea konna kathempu hi ding chule ka maicham chunga thilto ding, gimnamtui halding chule kamasanga thempu sangkhol chol kivon’a, kakin tong ding’a kalhendoh nahi hilou ham? Chule Israel chatea konna kimudoh keidinga thilto jouse chu napa insung mite kapeh dohsa ahitai. \x + \xo 2:28 \xt Potdohbu 28:1-4; \xt Thempu Dan 7:35,36\x*
\s1 Eli Thempu Insung Gihna
\p 
\v 29 Achutia ahileh ipi dinga kaumna a kathupeh gankilhaina le kathilto napai manga, kami Israel te thilpeh jousea konna ahoipen chun nathaodoh sah na dinga keisanga nachapa teni naja boljoh ham? Kami Israel te thilto aphalai laiya chu nangho kivah thaochet nahiu hitam?” ati.
\v 30 “Hijeh a chu Pakai Israel Pathen'in hitin aseiye, keiman nangma Levi insungle napa insung chu imatih chana kathempu a pang diu ahi tia nasei sa ahin, ahinlah keima eija a chu keiman jong ama chu kaja ding ahi, chule keima giltah’a eibol louva chu keiman jong kakhohsah louding ahi.
\v 31 Phat ahung lhunge, vetan, Keiman na thaneina kasuh bei nading nikho ahung nai tul tule, Hiteng chule nain sunga pasal tehse khat chabeh jong hung umlou ding ahiye.
\v 32 Hiche phatteng chule Israel te kipe haona chu nangman ngaicha geova, namit lhilha lha a nahin vet ding ahi chujongleh na insunga konna pasal ateh’a thi khatna khat cha jong umdoh louding ahitai.
\v 33 Ahingdoh chasun jong gim hesoh thoh'a umdiu, chule achate hou jong thise jenga thi diu ahi.
\v 34 Kathusei ho adih avetsahna chu, ka thusei ho chu hung guilhung ding, hichu nacha teni chunga hunglhung ding, Hophni chule Phinehas, nikhat sunga ani lhon’a thi ding ahi! \x + \xo 2:34 \xt 1 Samuel 4:11\x*
\v 35 Chutengleh keiman tahsan umtah thempu eijen ding leh kalung deitah bolding katundoh ding ahi. Ainsung jeng jong katundoh peh a, chule amaho chu kaleng tundoh ho thempu a tonsot a pang dingu ahi.
\v 36 Chuteng na insung’a ahing chengse a angsunga bohkhup uva, paisa le an athum diu, “Lungset tah in” tia asei diu, natoh ding neipeuvin, thempuho lah ah, chuteng keihon neh ding kham neitavinge, atidiu ahi,” ati.
\c 3
\s1 Samuel Pakaiyin Akou
\p 
\v 1 Hiti chun, Chapangpa Samuel chun Eli thempu noiya lhacha na atong jingin ahi. Hiche nikho phatlai chun Pakaiya konna thu hung kiphong chu ahahlheh jeng tai, chule themgao mu nei’ah a jongaum vah vah tapon ahi.
\v 2 Eli thempu in kho amuthei beh talou ahin, jankhat hi alupna ah aimutan ahi chule Samuel jong chu aimutan ahi.
\v 3 Pathen thaomei kide jong chu kisumit loulai ahin, Samuel vang chu ponbuh sunga aimutan ahi. Alupna chu Pathen thingkong komtah ahi.
\v 4 Photlot louvin Pakaiyin, “Samuel” tin ahin koutan ahile, “Hoiyo, Ipi thu hitam?” tin ana donbut in ahi.
\v 5 Ama athoudoh in Eli komlang ah alhaiyin, “Hiche ah kaum'e neikouvem?” aga tin ahile, Eli thempu jong, “Kakoupoi, nalupna ah chekit tan,” tin adonbut’in ahile ama jong achekit tai.
\v 6 Hichun Pakaiyin Samuel chu, “Samuel” tin ahin koukittai. Samuel jong athoudoh kit in Eli kom'a achekit in, “Hiche ah kaum'e neikouvem?” agatin ahi. Eli in jong hitin asei kit in, “Chapa kakoupoi, nalupna che kittan,” ati.
\v 7 Samuel in Pakai ahi ding chu ahetlou ahi ajeh chu hitobang Pakai kouna chu anajah khah loulai ahi.
\v 8 Chuin Pakaiyin thumvei channan ahinkou kit in, Samuel athou doh in Eli thempu chu aga dong kit in, “Hiche ah kaum'e neikou vem?” ati. Chuin Eli in Pakai kouna ahi ding kichen tah in ahetai.
\v 9 Chuin Samuel jah ah hitin aseipeh in, “Galum kit inlang, ijem tia nahung kikou kit’a ahileh, ‘Pakai seijin nalhachapa keiman kangaiye’” tin aseipeh tai, hichun Samuel jong ajalkhun lam ah akile kittai.
\v 10 Chule Samuel henga Pakai ahungin, “Samuel! Samuel!” tin akouvin ahile, Samuel in, “Seijin nalhacha pa keiman kangaiye,” tin adonbut tan ahi.
\v 11 Chuin Pakaiyin Samuel kom'a, “Ven keiman Israel sunga thil khat kabol ding, ahin hichun aja jouse nakhang asut ding ahi.
\v 12 Hiche nikho chule Eli insung douna a kasei jouse chu abulla kipat’a achaina geiya kaguilhun sah sohkei ding ahi.
\v 13 Keiman thutanna hi ama le a insung mite chunga thu katan ding ahi, tithu thu kapeh ahitai, hichu a imatih chana ding ahi, ajeh chu acha tenin Pathen ataitom lhonin, chule aman jong gihsalna aneipon ahi.
\v 14 Hijeh chun keiman Eli le acha teni chonsetna chu ka ngaidam louding, kilhai na le pumgo thilto ho a kisucham joulou ding ahitai,” ati.
\s1 Samuel In Pakai’a Dinga Thu Asei
\p 
\v 15 Samuel alupna ah jingkah chan geiyin aumdentai, Chuin ponbuh sunga kon'in ahung thoudoh in kot ahin hongdoh in, athujah ho seidoh ding akicha behseh in ahi. Pakai thusei chengho seidoh ding chu hahsa asa lheh in ahi.
\v 16 Ahinlah Eli in akouvin, “Kacha Samuel,” tia agah kouleh, “Kei hicheah kaumnai,” tin Samuel in adonbut in ahi.
\v 17 “Pakaiyin nakom'a ipi asei em? Abonchan imchah umlouvin nei seipeh in, ijem tia naim a naseidoh louva ahile Pathen mi jepna lePathen a konna thina na chunga chu mai tahen,” ati.
\v 18 Chuin Samuel in Eli kom'a abonchan aseipeh sohkei tai, imacha aseidoh lou aum tapoi. Hichun Eli thempun jong, “Hiche hi Pathen phatsah ahi,” tin aphongdoh in ahi.
\v 19 Samuel ahung khandoh toh lhonin Pakaiyin aumpin ahi. Chule thil ijakai Samuel in asei jouse aguilhung sohkei in ahi.
\v 20 Chule Israel mipite jouse, Dan a kipat chunglam Beersheba chengeijin ahen, Samuel Pathen themgao ahitai ti suhdet ahitai.
\v 21 Pakai Pathen jong Shiloh mun ah akilah jing jengin, Ponbuh sungah Samuel themgao kom'ah thu alhut in, chule Samuel in Israel mipi te lah a ale lhut kit jin ahi.
\c 4
\s1 Philistine Ten Pathen Thingkong Alah Peh
\p 
\v 1 Hiche phat laiya chu Israel te le Philistine mite kikah-a gal kidouna uma ahi. Israel sepai hon Ebenezer kom'a ngahmun uma ahi, chule Philistine ten Aphek mun-a ngahmun aneiyu ahi.
\v 2 Philistine ten Israel mite gallin ahin nokhum un ahile Israel sepai ten ana lal’un mi sangli jen ana that tauve.
\v 3 Chuin gal kisat akichaiya mipite a ngahmun ahung lhunphat un, Israel upaho chun, “Ipi jeh a tunia Pakaiyin Philistine masanga gal eilalsah u hintem?” Chuin ama hon aseiyun, “Shiloh a kon'in Pakai kitepna thingkong chu eiho dingin gapudoh uhitin, hichu ilahuva ahung lhun tengleh, hichun igalteuva kon'in eihuhdoh thei tauvinte,” akitiuvin ahi.
\v 4 Hijeh chun ama hon Shiloh’a Pakai kitepna van gam sepaite, Cherub vantil teni kikah’a cheng, Pathen thingkong pudingin mi asol’un, chule Eli chateni Hophni le Phinehas chu Pathen kitepna thingkong chutoh ahung lhon khom’in ahi. \x + \xo 4:4 \xt Potdohbu 25:22\x*
\v 5 Chutah chun Pakai thingkong chu Israel te ngahmun ahung lhun amu phat un, akiphah lheh jengun, akipanau aogin chun leiset ahotling leuvin ahi.
\v 6 Hichun, “Ipi soh hitam?” tin Philistine miten adong uvin, “Gingleng lunga a ao gin’u ajah phat’un, Hebrew mite ngahmun ging leng lung khu ipithu hitam?” akitiuve. Chuin ama hon Pakai kitepna thingkong ngahmun hunglhung ahi ti ahechen tauve.
\v 7 Amaho alung linglao tauvin ahi. “Pathen ngahmun uva ahunglhung tai,” tin asam’un, akicha tauvin ahi. Chuin amaho penguvin, “Ohe! Hiche hi vangsetna ahi!” Tumasanga chu hitobang thil hi ana um khalouhel ahi.
\v 8 “Hitobang hat tah Israel Pathen a konna kon eihuhhing jou diu ham? Nei panpiuvin! Egypt gam'a gamthip a hivei jouse sugama Pathen ho chu ahiuve.
\v 9 Hitobang kisatna anaum khapoi, Philistine! Ihatlou-ule Hebrew mite soh a ium diu ahi, pasal bangindingun, chule sat’un,” akitiuve.
\v 10 Chuin Philistine ten jong nasatah in gal asat’un ahile, Israel mite chu ajou un mihem tamtah jong athat tauvin ahi. Hiche nikho chun Israel te mi sang somthum athiuvin, athimoh chengse chu a ngahmun lamah ajam tauvin ahi.
\v 11 Pathen kitepna thingkong jong alahpeh’un, Eli chapa teni Hophi le Phinehas jong chu athat tauvin ahi.
\s1 Eli Thempu Thi
\p 
\v 12 Benjamin phung mikhat galmun a kon'in ahung lhailut in, hiche ni mama chun Shiloh ahunglhungin, apon taldeh duh le aluchung’a leisetnat dehduh pumin ahung lhailut in, hichun agentheina avetsah ahi.
\v 13 Eli chu lam pama touna chung khat’a touva anavet ahin, chule thuso chu ajah nom ahi, Ajeh chu Kitepna thingkong akipohdoh jeh’u chun alungsung akithing in ahi. Chule hiche mipa khopi sunga hunglut phat chun thusoh chu aseijin ahile, khopi pumpi miho chu hakan akap tauvin ahi.
\v 14 “Hiche awgin kithong khu ipi ham,” tin Eli in adongin ahile, thupopa chun Eli chu thusoh chu aseipeh tai.
\v 15 Eli chu tehse kum somko le get, amit in kho mulou ahitai.
\v 16 Aman Eli heng’ah, “Keima tutah’a chu galmun'a konna hung’ah kahi, keimat ah tuni tah’a hia chu uma kahi,” ati. Hichun Eli in, “Ipi iti nam?” tin adonge.
\v 17 Hichun thupopan, “Israel ten Philistine te chu alal tai, mipite akisat chaptai chule nacha teni Hophni le Phinahas jong athat tauve chujongleh Pathen Thingkong jong ala tauve,” tin ana donbut in ahi.
\v 18 Thupopan Pathen thingkong ala taove ti thucheng ajah jah chun Eli thempu atouna kelkot pang langah a kon'in akileh lhan a ngongpi gu akitaboh in athitai, ajeh chu ama chu ateh lheh tan chuke atahsa gih jong apohlal lheh ahi. Ama chun kum somli jen Israel te thutan vaihom ajong anapang ahi.
\v 19 Eli thempu mounu, Phinehas inneipi, naovop ahin, anao pen nading naija ahitan, ainneipu thile atehpu thi chule Pathen thingkong kipohmang thu ajah jah chun naoso nat’in ahin phan anavah pai pai jin ahi.
\v 20 Amanu chu naopen nat-in athitai, ahinlah athi masangin naodom nun atilkhou vin alhamon in, “Kicha hihin, Pasal naosen khat naneiye,” ati peh’e. Ahinlah amanun ima ana donbut thei tapoi.
\v 21 Naosen min chu Ichabod asahtai, (Loupina hoiya um hitam? tina ahi), ajeh chu, “Israel loupina chu akiladoh tai.” Amanun hiche min asahpeh najeh chu Pakai thingkong min akipohmang jeh le, atehpu le ainneipu athi tah jeh a asah ahi.
\v 22 Hiti chun amanun Pathen thingkong alah mang peh jeh uva, “Loupina chu Israel tetoh kikhen kang ahitai,” tia asei ahi.
\c 5
\s1 Pathen Thingkong Philistine Gam'a Atham
\p 
\v 1 Philistine ten Pathen thingkong alah jouvun, Ebenezer galmun'a kon'in Ashdod khopi alhut tauve.
\v 2 ama hon Pathen thingkong chu apu-uvin Dagon milim houna inah akoitauve,
\v 3 Ahin ajing jingkah matah in Ashdod khosung miten agavet ule Dagon chu Pakai thingkong masang ah chun amaichang tol lang ana ngan ana lhun ahi. Chuin ama hon Dagon chu aphongding un, akitunna ma ma a chun akoikit tauvin ahi.
\v 4 Ahin ajing jingkah in angai ngaiyin, Dagon chu Pakai thingkong masang ah chun amai tol lang ana ngan ana lhu kit in ahi. Tuchungin vang, akhutphang teni le aluchang chu tanbohsan kotbul lamah ana um'in, Dagon atahsa bou chu kitup chet in ana kijam in ahi.
\v 5 Hijeh chun Dagon thempupa hihen lang, koi hijongleh Ashdod khoa Dagon insunga hung jouse chun Dagon kijamna mun chu akeng’a ana chotpha louhel u ahi.
\v 6 Hijeh chun Pakai khut gih tah chu Ashdod mite chungah gih tah in achun, chule amaho le akho kom'a kho ho chung’a chun tijat umtah in abol genthei lheh tan ahi,
\v 7 Hichu mipiten ahetdoh phat’un, akapjah jengun, “Eihon Pathen thing khong ikomuva ikoi sot theilou diu ahi! Ama chu eihotoh kidou ahi bouve,I-Pathen'u Dagon toh eisuh mangtha diu ahi bouve,” atiuvin ahi.
\v 8 Hijeh chun ama hon Philistine milen milal jouse aheng uvah akou khom un, “Israel Pathen thingkong hi i-ilodiu hitam?” atiuve. Chuin mipiten adonbut’un, Israel Pathen Thingkong chu Gath lamah kipo tahen tin akinopto tauvin ahi. Hijeh chun ama hon Israel Pathen thing khong chu Gath lamah apolut tauve.
\v 9 Pathen thingkong Gath a agalhun phat un, Pathen khut thahat gihtah chu mite chunga achun, khopi sunga mite chu alen aneo abonchauvin ajep’in, uilut alansah tan ahi.
\v 10 Hijeh chun ama hon Pathen thingkong chu Ekron khopi ah atoldoh kit tauve, ahin Ekron miten amu phat un akapjah kit jengun, ama hon Israel Pathen thingkong ahin thahlut jengu hi, eiho hi thigam nao hen, eitiuva ahi atiuve.
\v 11 Hichun mipite hon Philistine lamkai ho thu apeuvin, ngehna aneiyun, “Lungset tah in Israel Pathen thingkong hi agamlang uva nathahlut pehlou uva ahileh Iboncha uva eitha gam dingu ahi,” akitiuve. Ajeh chu hihe khopi jouse sunga chu suhgamna nasatah uma ahitan, Pathen khut chu gihsatah chua ahitai.
\v 12 Mihem athimoh ho chunga chun uilut achun, chule khopia kon awgin hung gin chun Van chan alhungin ahi.
\c 6
\s1 Philistine Ten Pathen Thingkong Anung Le
\p 
\v 1 Pathen thingkong lha sagi jen Philistine gam'a aga tham in ahi.
\v 2 Philistine mihon thempuho le gaothem miho akoukhom uvin, hitin ana donguvin, “Pakai thingkong chung chang thu hi i-kalo diu hitam? Aumna ngaiya iti kasol diu ham? neisei peh’uvin,” atiuve.
\v 3 “Israel Pathen thingkong chu, nathah tengule thilpeh toh thah thauvin,” tin aseipeh un ahi. “Chonset thilto nato dingu chutileh natna chu kitang ding ahi, chuteng nadam uva, kitoldoh theilou natna chu Pathen khut ahi ti nahin hetdiu ahi,” atiuve.
\v 4 Hichun ama hon, “Itobang chonset thilto kabol diu ham?” tin ana dongun ahile, ama hon adonbut’un, “Hiche natna chun nangho le na vaipo nga ho na bonchau chunga achuh jeh chun, nang hon Sana tum nga le sana a kisem jucha nga, na gamsung u sunohphah dungjuijin sem’un.
\v 5 Hijeh chun gamsung suse na uilut lim le na jucha lim’u chu nasemuva chule Israel Pathen chu loupina napeh dingu ahi. Chuti henlang hileh, nangho leh na Pathen hou chule nagam uva kon'in akhut ahin jangkhaisah dom ding ahi.
\v 6 Nalung-tahsah hih un chule doulung jong puhih un, Pharaoh le Egypt mite bangin lung puhih un. Pathen'in thilkidang abol ho jeh a hung potdoh ahibou-uve.
\v 7 Tun bongkang thah sem uvin lang bongpi namkolyon pokhalou lai hel anou noichep lai cheh ni gakaiyun chule bongpi teni chu bongkang thah chu kai sah’un, anou teni vang chu akom lhona kon'in inlam ah hin nung kai tauvin,” ati.
\v 8 “Pakai thingkong chu bongkang chunga chun tungdoh unlang akom'a chun chonset thilpeh dinga thilto sana tum, sana a kisem jucha lim le uilut lima kisem jong chu nasem thadiu, chutengleh bongpi teni chu soldoh unlang achena nom nom’ah che tauhen.
\v 9 Igamsung’u akhokal Beth-shemesh lang ajot a ahile gentheina te ho hin Pathen khut a kon ahi ti hiche a konna chu hetthei ahi, amavang ache lou tah’a ahivangle, igamnao chu ama khut ahipoi ti kihetdoh na ahi,” atiuve.
\v 10 Chuti chun aki seipeh nao bang bang chun abol tauvin ahi, bongpi noitwi neilai ni kaisah dingin agongun bongnou teni vang chu ajaosah pouve.
\v 11 Chuti chun Pakai thingkong chule chonset thilto sana jucha lim le uilut lim sana tum jong chu bongkang chunga chun akoi tauvin ahi.
\v 12 Chuin bongpi teni chu jangkeiyin Beth-shemesh geiyin achelhung keilhonin ahi. Philistine mipite lamkaihon Beth-shemesh gamgi chen geiyin ahinjui lhung peh un ahi.
\v 13 Chule Beth-shemesh mihon phaichama chu suhlou chang ana at laitah u ahin, akhodah uva ahile Pakai thingkong ahung lhun amu phat’un, hapan akipah lheh jeng tauve.
\v 14 Bongkang chu Joshua kitipa loulaiya songpi kom'a ahung kingan chuin mipite hon
\p bongkang thing meiya tidingin avo lhauvin, bongpi teni chu athat’un Pakaiya govamna maicham asem un ahi.
\p 
\v 15 Levi phungmi phabep khat in Pakai thingkong chule akom'a thingkong, sana jucha limle sanatum uilut lim jong chu alalhauvin songpi chunga chun akoijun ahi. Hiche govamna maicham ho chu Pakaiya dingin asem’un ahi.
\v 16 Philistine lamkailen mi nga in thil kibol ho jouse chu amusohkei uvin chule hicheni mama chun Ekron ah akile kit tauve.
\v 17 Chule Philistine miten Pakai henga chonset thilto dinga ahin nungsol’u sana uilut lim, sana tum nga ho chu: Ashdod akon khat, Gath akon khat, Gaza akon khat, Ashkelon akon khat chule Ekron a konna khat cheh ahi.
\v 18 Chule sana jucha limho chun Philistine khopi ngaho, chule akimvella khoneoho, gamvaipo nga gamvaipoh na noiya umho vetsahna a ahin thot u ahi. Beth-shemesh khoa Joshua loulaiya songpi lentah khat’a bongkang chu asolhah nau chu tujenginjong imatih chan geiya hettohsah na dingin aum jing nalaiye.
\s1 Thingkong Kiriath-Jearim’a Apohlut-U
\p 
\v 19 Ahinlah Beth-shemesh a kon mihon thingkong sung avet jeh un mi som sagi Pakaiyin athat tai. Hiti chun Pakai natoh kidang chun mipite nasatah in alunghem lheh jeng tauvin ahi.
\v 20 “Hiche Pathen theng masanga hi koiham adingjou ding’ah?” tin mipin asam’un “Thingkong chi hoiya itoldod diu hitam?” tin akidong tauve.
\v 21 Hijeh chun thupodin Kiriath-jearim mipite henga mi asollun, “Philistine miten Pakai thingkong chu ahung thahlut tauve, hungun lang, hung kilah’un,” tin thu apohsah tauvin ahi.
\c 7
\p 
\v 1 Hijeh chun Kiriath-jearim mite chu ahung uvin Pakai thingkong chu ahung kilah tauve. Ama hon Pakai thingkong chu thinglhang lama Abinadab inah alhut’un, achingtup dingin Eleazer achapa ngansena anei tauve. \x + \xo 7:1 \xt 2 Samuel 6:2-4; 1 Thusimbu 13:5-7\x*
\v 2 Thingkong chu phat sottah kum somni vel Kiriath-jearim mun'a um ahi. Hiche phatsung chun Israel pumpi chu ana lunghem lheh jeng uve, ajeh chu ama hon Pakaiyin nampi chu adalhah bang’a a agel u ahi.
\s1 Samuel In Israel te Galjonaa Alamkai
\p 
\v 3 Chuin Samuel in Israel pumpi jah ah, “Nangho atahbeh a Pakai heng lam’a hung kile nom mong nahiule, nangho lah a um gamchom mite indoi Ashtoreth chu paidoh un, chule Pakaiya dingin nalung sung’u kigong tup unlang, ama bou jen’un chutileh Aman Philistine mite a konna nahuhdoh thei diu ahi,” ati.
\v 4 Hijeh chun Israel miten jong amahoa um Baal chule Ashtoreth gamchom mite indoi chu apaidoh’un, Pakai jengbou ahou tauve.
\v 5 Chuin Samuel in, “Israel mite jouse na boncha uvin Mizpah mun’ah hung kikhom un, chutengleh keima nangho dingin tao vinge,” ati.
\v 6 Hijeh chun Israel mite jong Mizpah mun’ah akikhom khom’un, Pakai hounan twi agathal uvin Pakai angsunga asung lhauvin, hiche nikho chun an angol uvin, Pakai douna a achonset nau akisihun ahi. (Hiche Mizpah mun'a chu Samuel Israel te thutanna ahung pang na chu ahi).
\v 7 Philistine lamkai hon Israel mite Mizpeh mun’ah akikhom uve tithu ajah phat’un, asepai ho akigon tupsah’un ahi. Philistine miten eihin nai tauve ti ajah phat’un Israel mite jong akicha lheh jeng’un ahi.
\v 8 “Pakai Pathen'in Philistine te khut a konna eihuhdoh na diuva, taona’a ilhahsam louhel diu ahi,” tin Samuel kom'ah ngehna ahung neijuve.
\v 9 Chuin Samuel in kengoinou khat alan Pakai hengah todohna pumgo thilto maicham asem’in ahi. Aman Israel mite taopehna aneiyin, Pathen'in ataona asanpeh tan ahi.
\v 10 Samuel in hiche govam thilto abollaijin, Philistine te chu Israel te sat dingin ahung naijun, ahi. Ahinlah Pakaiyin kidangtah in van aginsah in, keh alhah sah in, hiche nikho chun Philistine te boinan alhun den’un, Israel chaten galjona anei tauve.
\v 11 Chuin Israel te chu Mizpah a kon'in apotdoh’un, Philistine te chu anungdal’un, Beth-car aphah kahseu vin athat tou peh’un ahi.
\v 12 Chuin Samuel in songtumlen khat alan Mizpah le Jeshanah kikah ah aphut’in, aman
\p hiche mun chu EBENEZER asah’in ahi. Ajeh chu, “Hilai mun chan’ah Pathen'in ei kithopiuve,” ati.
\p 
\v 13 Hijeh chun phat chomkhat sungin Philistine miten Irael mite ahin nokhum tapouve. Chule Samuel phatlai sungsen, Pathen thahat najallin Philistne mite anem lhauvin ahi.
\v 14 Chule Philistine miten Israel mite’a analahpeh’u, Ekron chule Gath kom'a khopi analah ho jong Israel te alepeh kittan, chule agam kimvel jouse jong chu Philistine te khutna kon'in Israel ten alelah kit tauvin ahi. Chule Israel mite le Amon mite kah’a chamna aumin ahi.
\s1 Samuel Israel te Thutan Vaihom’a Apan
\p 
\v 15 Chule Samuel in adamlai sungin Israel mite thu ana tan’in ahi.
\v 16 Akumseh leh gamsung akhol kimvellin, Bethel le Gilgal, chule Mizpah a ache velkol
\p jingin ahi. Aman Israel mite chungah, adeh in hiche munho lah a hin thu anatan jin ahi.
\p 
\v 17 Chule Ramah kho’a ain aum jeh chun ain’ah ahung kilejin, chule Israel te thu anatan jin ahi. Chule Samuel in Ramah a chun Pakaiya dingin maicham khat asemin ahi
\c 8
\s1 Israel ten Leng Angeh’u
\p 
\v 1 Samuel ateh lheh tan ahile, Israel lah a thutan vaihom ding’in achapa te apansah tai.
\v 2 Joel le Abijah chu achate lah a akum tampen teni ahi lhon'e, amani Beersheba khopi’ah thutan vaihom’in apang lhone.
\v 3 Ahivangin apa toh abang lhonpoi, sum lam’ah akitah lhonpoi. Amanin sum nehguh pou abol lhonin, thu adih in atanji lhon tapoi.
\v 4 Achai’nan Israel upaho jouse chu Ramah kho’ah Samuel toh lunggel khomna anei juvin ahi.
\v 5 ama hon, “Ven, nangla nateh lheh jengtan, nachate jong nang toh abang lhonpon, Leng khat neipeuvin namdang ten anei banga thutan dingin,” atin aseipeh un ahi. \x + \xo 8:5 \xt Danbu Ni Na 17:14\x*
\v 6 Samuel vang chu athil ngaichat’u chung’ah chun alung alhaipoi, hijeh chun panpi ngaichan Pakai kom'a ache’in ahi.
\v 7 Pakaiyin Samuel jah a, “Nakom'a asei jouseu bolpeh in, nang napaiju ahipoi, keijoh eipaiju ahi bouve, ama hon kei eidei lou u ahi bouve, aleng diuva eidei lou u ahi,” tin adonbut tan ahi.
\v 8 “Egypt gam'a konna kahin puidoh uva kipat’na gamchom mite indoi bou ahou nom jo uve. Tua jong hitobangma achu nang jong nabollu ahi bouve,” ati.
\v 9 “Asei jouseu chu bolpeh in, ahinlah leng khat in achung uva vai ahin hopna ding thua hin, kaangkhen chan gihsallin,” atipeh tai.
\s1 Samuel In Israel Chate Agihsal
\p 
\v 10 Hijeh chun Samuel in, Pakaiya konna gihna thuchang ho chu Israel mite chu leng athumnao chungthu’ah chun aban ban’in ahetsah tan ahi.
\v 11 Samuel Israel te jah ah, “Leng nahin nei uva aman nachung’uva lengvai ahin hop tengleh, Leng in nachateu chu alah a sakol kangtalai ho leh sakol sepai dinga, chule sakol kangtalai masanga lhai dinga,
\v 12 Abangkhat chu sepai lah a jalamkai chule lamkai napeh dingu, abang kit chu pumthou chang loukaiya apan sah dingu, abangkhat chu kangtalai ase ho sema napan sah diu ahi,” ati.
\v 13 “Lengpan nachanu teu amat uva anhon'a apansah uva, abang chu changlhah kang a apansah diu chujongleh abangkhat chu thao namtui sem’a apansah uva soh’a anei diu ahi.
\v 14 Nalou phalai ho jouse nalahpeh uva lengpithei lei le olive leija abol uva athao alah tengu leh atohkhompi ho apeh ding’u ahi.
\v 15 Aman na chang-ga le lousoh ho a konna som’a khat alah ding chule vaibolla pang ho leh sohte ho apeh ding’u ahi.
\v 16 Aman napasal houle, numei ho soh dia akimat a, chule nagancha hoilai lai ho ama dinga akilah ding ahi.
\v 17 Aman na ganchahon ho jeng’a jong som’a khat angeh ding, nachamlouva napeh ding ahi.
\v 18 Chuche nikho chuleh nang hon nakilhen’u lengpa jeh a chu nahung ka diu chule Pakaiyin naka gin’u nangaipeh lou diu ahi,” tin aseipeh tai.
\v 19 Ahivangin mipite ho chun, “Hijeng jongleh Leng chu kadei nalaiyuve,” tin Samuel thusei chu angaisah dehpouvin ahi.
\v 20 Hichun mipi ho chun, “Kakimvel uva gamdang ho bangin, kalengpau vin kachung uva thutan hen, gal kisat jeng’a jong hin eilamkai uhen,” ati tauvin ahi.
\v 21 Hichun Samuel in Pakai kom’ah mipi ho thusei chu aseipeh kit in ahile,
\v 22 Pakaiyin, “Asei bang bang u chun bolpeh inlang, Leng chu petan,” ati. Hichun Samuel jong anom’in mipi te ho chu ainlam cheh uva anung soltan ahi,
\c 9
\s1 Saul In Samuel Akimupi
\p 
\v 1 Hichelai chun Benjamin chilhah mihaotah le mijong thu-nunjou mi khat aumin, ama chu Aphiah chapa, Becorath chapa, Zeror chapa, Abiel chapa, amin Kish kiti khat anaum'inahi.
\v 2 Kish hin chapa khat aniyin, amin Saul ahi, ama chu gollhang phatah le mel-hoitah ahin, chule alengkouva lhah chunglamsen midang akhokhel sohkeiyin in, Israel chate lah a jong chun ama tobang koima ana umpoi.
\v 3 Nikhat hi Kish sangan ho chu ana vahdoh in ahile, Kish in achapa Saul jah a, “Nasoh ho khat kipuijin lang sanganho hollin kipat doh tan,” ati.
\v 4 Hijeh chun Saul in asohho khat akipuiyin, Ephraim gamsunga Shalishah gamkol sungle akimvel sung chule Benjamin molsang dung jouse achon lhonin ahinlah amujoulhon pon ahi.
\v 5 Achainan amani Zuph gam ahunglhun lhon phat in Saul in sohpa jah ah, “Hung in, in lam’ah kile tahite, achuti louva ahile eini le sanganho jeh in, kapa ana lungkhamval get inte,” ati.
\v 6 Ahinlah sohpan, “Ipi ham khat kalung’ah ahung kilange! Hichea hin Pathen mikhat aumin, hiche khopia hi cheng ahin,ama chu miho jousen jana sangtah apeh ahi, aman asei sei chu dih jeng ahi. Che hitin ama chu gaholdoh hite, ijehnem-itile iche nading lampi eiseipeh theilhon ahi,” ati.
\v 7 Hichun Saul in adonbut “Ama peh ding la imacha i-neilhon pon, i-neh lhon ding an jouse la akichai gamtan, ama peh dingima ineilhon poi,” ati.
\v 8 Ahinla asohpan, “Aphai, keiman kakhut ah dangka neokhat kaneiye, Pathen mipa chu hiche hi pe hitin chule ipi soh’em vehite,” ahinti.
\v 9 (Hiche phatlai chun, Pathen a konna hung kisei angai dinga ahile, “mitva neipa kom'a cheuhitin, gadong’u hite,” atijiuvin ahi).
\v 10 Hichun Saul in asohpa jah a, “Adihe, hiti chun gabol bol hite,” tin ana nom in ahi. Hichun hiche khopia mitva neipa holdin akipat doh lhontan ahi.
\v 11 Chuin lhang lang akaldoh lhon’a ahile, numei phabep twi-thal ding’a ahung amulhonin, amaho kom'a chun, “Tunin mitva neipa chu aumdem?” tin adonglhonin ahi.
\v 12 Hichun ama hon ahin donbut lhonin “Henge, hiche lampi jetlam’a chelhon lechun, ama chu khopi kelkot phung kom'a chu um ding ahi. Mipi gan kilhaina’a ache ahung lhun pettah ahi” atiuvin ahi.
\v 13 An nedinga akaltou masangin, gangtah in che lhonin lang gakimupi vahlhonin, ajeh chu ahunglhun le gan kilhaina sa ho chu phatthei aboh tokah kahsea mipin an aneh theilou diu ahi,” atiuve.
\v 14 Chuin amani chu khopi sunga ahunglut lhon chun khopi kelkot agah jotpa lhon le Samuel chu Pathen houna mun’a dia ahung potdoh toh akitoh chet un ahi.
\v 15 Pakaiyin Samuel kom'a nikho masanga chu ana seipeh sa ahitan,
\v 16 “Jing nikho tuphat don leh Benjamin phung’a kipat’a pasal khat ka hinsol ding ahi. Aman kamite lah a lamkai dinga thao na nu ding ahi. Aman Philistine mite khut a konna Israel te ahuhdoh dingu, kamite kahin vetsuh’a khotona puma, chule akanao kangailhah ding ahi,” ati.
\v 17 Samuel in Saul amu phat’in, Pakaiyin ajah a, “Hiche mipa hi ahi kanasei chu, ama hin kamite alamkai ding ahi,” ati.
\v 18 Saul in Samuel kelkot phung lam’a ahin naipheiyin, “Mitvaneipa in chu hoilai ham? Neiseipeh thei ding ham?” tin anadongin ahi.
\v 19 Chuin Samuel in adongbut in,“Keima hi mitvaneipa chu kahi, chule Pathen houna mun'a ana kaltouvin, hia chun nei kimupin, hiche mun'a chu An ineh khom lhon ding chujongleh jingkah leh nahetnom ho chu naseipeh nange, chule nalampia nasol nange.
\v 20 Chule nithum masang’a sanganho avah mang hojeh chun lung kham hih in, hiho chu akimusa ahitai, nagelkhoh le nahetdia ka seipeh nom chu ahile nang le na insung mite hi Israel pumpin angeh’uva avet jing u chu nahi,” ati.
\v 21 Hichun Saul’in, “Keihi Israel phung lah a jong alhumpen, Benjamin phungmi kahin, ka-insung jong kaphung sung uva jong imacha loupen kahiuve, achutileh kei pen kom'a hitia hi ipi nasei nom ham?” ati.
\v 22 Chuin Samuel in Saul le asohpa chu kikhopna indan lentah sung khat’a ahin puilut’in, dokhong lubuhl lam, akikou lamkai somthum ho lah a mun loupi pena atousah tan ahi.
\v 23 Chuin Samuel in an-honpa jah a, “Nahenga atumbeh in koiyin tia kapeh sachan chu hin choitan,” ati.
\v 24 Chuin an-honpan sachan chu ahin choidoh’in, Saul angsung’ah aluipeh tan, hichun Samuel in Saul jah ah, “Na-angsung’a kiluiyah hiche sachan hi nang dia kiluiyah ahi, nen, akikou chengse to tua naneh khomdia kakhendoh ahi,” ati. Chuti chun hiche nikho chun Saul in Samuel toh anekhom in ahi.
\v 25 Chuin Pathen ahounao munsang a konna khopi sung ahung kumlhah phat’un, Samuel in Saul indan chung’ah alupna ding asempeh in ahi.
\v 26 Ajing jingkah matah in athouvun, chuin Samuel’in Saul indan chung’ah akou touvin, asoldoh theina dingin, “Thouvin,” ati.
\v 27 Chuin anigel lhonin in akon’in apotdoh khom lhonin khopi pam agei lhonin Samuel in Saul jah ah, “Nasohpa ana masajep dingin seijin, Pathen a konna thu hung kisei kahetsah theina dingin,” ati.
\c 10
\s1 Samuel In Saul Leng Dia Thao Anu
\p 
\v 1 Chuin Samuel in olive thao thei khat alan, Saul luchung’ah asunglhan achop’in ajah ah, “Keiman hiche kabolna ajeh chu Pakaiyin nangma Israel chunga lamkai dinga, panmun sanga dinga nalhendoh ahitai.
\v 2 Tunia hi nangma keija konna napotdoh tengleh, Benjamin gamgi Zelzah-a Rachel lhan kom'a mini namu ding, sangan ho chu akimutai ti chu amanin aseilhon ding ahi. Napa sangan ho jeh a nalungkhamnachu akichaitan, tua hi nangni dinga lungkham ah ahi. Aman miho jah ah kachapa namu uvem tin adongle le in ahi,” ati.
\v 3 “Chule chua kon chun chebe-lhon lechun, Tabor phaicham lhungin natin chua chun Bethel’a Pathen henga chetouva mithum nakimutopi ding, khat pan kelcha nou thum, khatpan changlhah thum chule khatpan lengpitwi haikhat achoi namu ding ahi.
\v 4 Chule amaho chun chibai naboh diu, changlhah ni napeh dingu, hichu akhut uva konna nakisan ding ahi.
\v 5 Chutengleh Phlistine sepaiho umna Pathen lhaang’a chu nahung ding, chule hiche kho pia chu nahung tengleh tumging, khongcha, kuli, selangdah, amasang uva hintho’a munsang’a konna hung kumlha themgao honkhat nakitopi ding, amaho chun gaothu asei dingu ahi.
\v 6 Hiche phatteng chule Pakai Lhagao thahat tah’a nachung’uva hung chu ding, amahotoh gaothu nasei khom ding, chule michombeh khat nakiso ding ahi,” ati.
\v 7 “Chule hiche melchihna ho hi nachung’a ahunglhun tengleh, Pathen'in naumpi jeh chun Pathen'in napuina lam lam chu bol jengin.
\v 8 Chutengleh nangma keisangin Gilgal’a nachesuh ding, chule hikom’a chu ikimu’a govam kilhaina le chamna thilto gan kilhaina bol ding’a iki suhto ding ahi. Nangman hikom'a’a chu nisagi chan nei nga ding chule maban a nathilbol ding ka seipeh ding nahi,” ati.
\s1 Samuel Melchihna Ho Aguilhun
\p 
\v 9 Hiti chun Saul chu, Samuel’a konna kinungle dinga ache got chun, Pathen'in ama lungchom khat apen, Hiche ni chun melchihna jouse chu aguilhung sohtai.
\v 10 Saul le asohpa Gilgal’a ahunglhun lhon phat’in, ama hon themgao thah loi khat amaho langa ahung amu phat un, Pathen Lhagao thahat tah in Saul chung’ah ahung chun, ama tah jong chun gaothu aseiyin ahi.
\v 11 Chuin Saul anahe ho chun, “Kish chapa, Saul jeng jong themgao hihi ngap hitam?” atiuve.
\v 12 Chule chukom'a ding miho lah khat’in, “Apateu itobang hijongleu, mijouse themgao hitheiya ham?” ati. Hichea pat a chu, “Saul jeng jong Themgao soh ngap hitam?” tia hung kiseipan ahi. \x + \xo 10:12 \xt 1 Samuel 19:23,24\x*
\v 13 Chuin Saul in gaothu aseijou phat’in, Pathen houna mun’ah ahung kaltouvin ahi.
\v 14 Chuin Saul pangah pan ama le asohpa jah a, “Hoiya nagache ham?” tia adoh leh “Sangan holla kache lhon ahin, ahinlah kamu lhonpon, Samuel dong dinga kache lhon ahi,” tin Saul in ana donbut’e.
\v 15 Apangah pan adong kit’in, “O Samuel in ipi naseipeh lhon em?” tin adongkit in ahi.
\v 16 Saul in adonbut in, “Sangan chu akimutai tin eina seipeh lhonin,” ahi. Ahinlah Saul in apangah kom'a Samuel in lenggam thu asei chu, asedoh poi.
\s1 Samuel In Saul Leng Dia Aphondoh
\p 
\v 17 Chujouvin Samuel in Pakai masang’ah Israel mipite jouse Mizpah mun'a kimuto din kouvin ahi.
\v 18 Ajah-uva, “Hiche hi Pakai Israel te Pathen phondoh ahi: Keiman Egypt a kon'in kahin puidoh un, chule Egypt mite’a kon'in kahin huhdoh un, chule namdang mite jouse bol gentheina a kon'in kahin hoidoh in,
\v 19 Ahin na genthei nauva konna kahuhdoh vangun, na Pathen’u tunin napai tauve chule hitin nasei’un, i-dang sangin leng khat kadei uve natiuve. Hijeh chun tun, naphung nachang uvin, na nampumpiu vin Pakai ang’ah dingin kigong un,” ati.
\v 20 Chuin Samuel in Israel phung jouse Pakai masang’ah ahin puikhom’in chule vang asangin Benjamin phung chu alhengtai.
\v 21 Benjamin phung insung jouse chu akoukhom kit in, chule amaho lah a chun Matri insung alhengdoh kit tan ahi. Achainan Kish cahpa Saul chu amaho insung lah a kon chun ana lhengdoh un ahi. Ahinlah ama chu ahol’u le aholmo tauve.
\v 22 Chuin ama hon Pakai adoh uleh, “Thilkeo lah a akiselle,” tin Pakaiyin ahin donbut’e.
\v 23 Hiti chun ama hon jong Saul chu agamudoh uvin ahin puidoh uva mipi lah a adinleh, alengkouva pat chunglamse chu mijouse sangin asangjon ahi.
\v 24 Chuin Samuel in mijouse jah ah, “Hiche mipa hi ahi Pakijin na lengpa ding uva alhen chu ahi, Israel te lah a ama tobang adang aumpoi,” ati. Chuin mipiten, “Lengpa damsot hen,” tin asam’un ahi.
\v 25 Chuin Samuel in mipite jah a lengpan atoh atham di thudol ahillin, chule lekhajol khat’a asun lut in, Pakai angsung'ah akoitai. Chuin Samuel in mipi ho chu ama ama incheh’ah asoltai.
\v 26 Chuin Saul jong Gibeah kho a-inlam ah achetan, chule Pathen'in alungsung atohkhah mi honkhat in alhon piuvin ahi.
\v 27 Ahinlah panna bei mi phabep chun, “Hiche pan iti eihuhdoh diu ham?” atiuve. Chuin ama hon ama nahsahmon abol’un, thilpeh imacha ahin choipeh pouvin ahi. Ahinlah ama athipbeh in ana nahsah pon ahi.
\c 11
\s1 Saul In Ammon Mite Ajo
\p 
\v 1 Lhakhat jouvin Ammon mi Nahash lengpa chun Jebesh-gilead khopi dou dingin ahung kon'in ahi. Chuin Jabesh khoa cheng mijouse chun Nahash jah-a, “Keiho toh kitepna khat sem uhitin chule nasoh kahi diu ahi,” tin atao tauve.
\v 2 Hichun Nahash in, “Aphai, ahinla aumdan khat sem uhite, Israel pumpi kajumso theinadia, namit changu jetlam cheh ka kaldoh ding ahi,” ati.
\v 3 Hichun ama hon, “Achutile nisagi nei ngah un, Israel gamsunga mi sol uvinge, eikithopi diu koima ahung louva ahileh naheng uvah lut tau vinge,” tin Jabesh upahon adonbut tauve.
\v 4 Thupoho Saul umna Gibeah ahunglhun phat’un, mijouse mitchang kaldoh ding thu ajahdoh phat in khopi sunga mijouse akapjah jeng tauvin ahi.
\v 5 Hiche pettah’a chu Saul chu louva konna ganchahon nunga hunga ahi, chule khopi ahunglhun phat’in, “Ipi thilsoh uma hitam? Ipi jeh a mipite hitobang tah’a khu kap-a hiuvem?” tin adongin ahile ama hon Jabesh thupole ho thu chu aseipeh tauve.
\v 6 Chuin Saul’in chuche thusoh ajah phat’in, Pathen a konna lhagao achungah ahung chun, alunghan nachu ahung koujah jengin ahi.
\v 7 Chuin bongchal ni athat’in, achanbong bongin, Israel gamkai jousea ahom dingin thupole ho asollin, “Samuel le Saul gal’a jui louva galkon lou jouse abongchal jouse hitia hi kichanpan ding ahi!” tin gih na jong aneiyin ahi. Chule Pathen'in Saul lunghan chun mijouse akichat sah in, kilungkhat tah in ahung kikhom sohkeijun ahi.
\v 8 Chuin Saul’in Bezek mun’ah akhom khomin ahile Israel a kon mi sang jathum, chule Judah a kon, mi sang somthum akhom doh in ahi.
\v 9 Saul in thupole ho chu Jabesh-Gilead miho henga, “Jing sunkim le kithopina namu diu ahi!” tin thu ale thot in ahile hiche thusoh ajah phat’un, khopi sungah kipana lentah ahunglhungin ahi.
\v 10 Jabesh mihon agal mite ho kom'ah “Jing teng naheng uva kahung diu ahin, kachung uva nabol nom chan nabol theiju ahi,” tin aseipeh tauvin ahi.
\v 11 Ahin, ajing jingkah matah in Saul ahung lhun’in, asepaite hopthum in ahom khen’in, khovah in amelmate ngahmun adelkhum’un, hiche jingkah sungse chun, Ammon mite athat in, ahingdoh chasun akithen cheh uvin, achang changing ajammang tauvin ahi.
\v 12 Chuin mipiten Samuel jah a, “Ipi jeh a Saul i-chung uva leng chang ding ham? tia seiho chu hoilai um gam uhi tam? Neipedoh un, that gam uvinge!” tin angeh un ahi.
\v 13 Ahin Saul in adonbutin, “Tunia hi mi khatcha kithat louding ahi, ajeh chu tuni hi Israel ahuhhing nikho ni ahi,” ati.
\v 14 Chuin Samuel in mipi jah ah, “Hungun Gilgal ah cheu hitin, ilengpau gaphongdoh kit uhite,” ati.
\v 15 Chuin mipite jouse chu Gilgal ah acheuvin, Pakai masang ah Saul chu Leng in asem doh tahbeh tauve. Hiti chun Pakai angsung'ah chamna, kilhaina thilto gantha abolluvin, Saul jong Israel mite jong hapan akipah sohkei juvin ahi.
\c 12
\s1 Samuel In Israel te Lhahna Thu Asei
\p 
\v 1 Chuin Samuel chun Israel pumpi jah dingin thu aseiyin, “Veuvin kahenga nasei jouseu kangaiyin, nachung uva vaihom ding leng khat jong kasempeh tauve.
\v 2 Naleng’u hi tun nalamkai-u jong ahitai, namasang laitah uva kadinge, kumtam tehse samkang kahitai. Kachapa te to nakiloi diu ahi. Kachapan laiya kipan in tuni chengeijin nalamkaiyun kahung pang in ahi.
\v 3 Tun hikom'a ka-ume, koi bongchal ahilou le koi sangan kalahpeh umkha em? Koi kalheplhah umkha em? Koi kasuhgenthei umkha em? Koi kom'a sumguh tholla kalahpeh umkha em? Pakai le athao nupa ang’ah kachung chang thu hettohsah pumin nei seipeh un, kana suhkhel aum jongleh tun sudih inge,” ati.
\v 4 Mipin adonbut’un, “Aumpoi, nangman nei joulhep kha pouve, nangman keihoa kon'in thil neocha jeng jong nalapoi,” atiuve.
\v 5 “Pakai le athaonu pa hi tunia na angsung laitah uva ahetoh ahi, kanung thu atheng’e” tin Samuel aphongdoh in ahi. Chuin mipin, “Henge ama hi ahetoh ahi,” tin adonbut uve.
\v 6 Samuel in abanjom ding, “Aaron le Mose anagong jong chu Pathen ahi, napu napa teu Egypt a konna ahin puidohpa chu Ama chu ahi,” ati. \x + \xo 12:6 \xt Potdohbu 6:26\x*
\v 7 “Hijeh chun, tun nangho le napu napa teu chunga Pakai thilkidang nasatah tah abol chengse geldoh sah u bang chun Pakai masanga nangho dingdet un,” ati.
\v 8 “Israel mite Egypt a aumlaiyun, Pakai henga akapun ahile, Aman Mose le Aaron Israel te chu Egypt gam'a kon'in ahin puidoh sah lhonin, hiche gam'a ahin lhut lhontai. \x + \xo 12:8 \xt Potdohbu 2:23\x*
\v 9 Ahivangin mipiten hetman louvin Pakai a Pathen-u asumil’un, aman Sisera, Hazor khopia sepai janel gal lamkai khut le Philistine te khut’a chule Moab lengpa khut’a apeh doh in ahi. \x + \xo 12:9 \xt Thutan Vaihom Ho 4:2; \xt Thutan Vaihom Ho 13:1; \xt Thutan Vaihom Ho 3:12\x*
\v 10 Chuin amaho Pakai henga akap’un, keihon Pakai kadalhau vin Baal lim le Ashtoreth kahou jeh un kachonse taove, ahinlah tun kamelma teu khut’a kon'in neihuhdoh uvin, chutileh nangma kajhou diu ahi atiuve. \x + \xo 12:10 \xt Thutan Vaihom Ho 10:10-15\x*
\v 11 Chutengleh, Pakaiyin Gideon, Bedan, Jephthah chule Samuel asol in muntin'a namel mate hou khut’a kon'in neihuhdoh’un lungmong in acheng tauvin ahi. \x + \xo 12:11 \xt Thutan Vaihom Ho 7:1; \xt Thutan Vaihom Ho 4:6; \xt Thutan Vaihom Ho 11:29; \xt 1 Samuel 3:20\x*
\v 12 “Pakai na Pathen-u chu na lengpao ahilaiyin, Ammon chate lengpa Nahash nangho douna-a ahung namu phat un, nang hon kahenga, ahipoi, leng khat in kachung uva vai ahomding ahi bouve natiuve, \x + \xo 12:12 \xt 1 Samuel 8:19\x*
\v 13 Tun veuvin, nang hon nalhen ule na ngaichat’u lengpa chu hikom'a aum'e chule veuvin, Pakaiyin nachung uva leng khat atungtai.
\v 14 Tun Pakai nagin uva chule nahou uva, chule athusei chu na ngai uva, nadoudal loubeh uva ahileh nangho le na lengpau vin Pakai chu Pathen ahi ti avetsah na ahitai.
\v 15 Ahinlah Pakai thusei chu nadoudal vang uleh, chule na ngaipeh lou uva ahivangle, akhut nachung uva gihsa ding, nang le namite chunga chu ding.
\v 16 Pakaiyin, thil lentah tah abol ding ho, tun dingdoh uvin lang ven,” ati.
\v 17 “Nanghon naheuve, tuphat hi suhlou chang at-lai ahin go ajuji pon ahi, ahin tao leng Pakaiyin van kithinsah in tin go ju ding ahi. Hiteng chule Pakai kom'a leng nathumu chu Ama douna melse tah a chonse nahiu kihet tauvin nate,” ati.
\v 18 Chuin Samuel in Pakai akouvin ahile, hiche nikho chun Pakaiyin vanginle keh ahin sol’in, hiti chun mipi chun Pakai le Samuel aging tauvin ahi.
\v 19 Mijouse chun Samuel hengah, “Pakai henga neitaopeh un, achuti louva ahileh kathigam diu ahi,” atiuve. “Tua hi leng ithum jeh uva chonset ikiholbe’u ahitai,” atiuve.
\v 20 Hichun Samuel in, “Kichahih uvin, nabol khel’u ahitai, ahinlah Pathen phaten dihtah in hou-uvin nalungthim pumpin houvun, chule kinungle kit bol hih’un,” atin ahi.
\v 21 “Nungchon hihbeh’un, nungchon a milim pao theilou ho chun napanpi louhel diu ahi, hiho chu panna bei jeng ahiuve.
\v 22 Pakaiyin amite itih hijongleh adalhah louhel ding ahi, ajeh chu adalhah a ahile ama amin lentah chu asuhminset ding ahi. Hijeh chun Pakaiyin nangho amite dia agot hi ama lunglhaina ahi,” ati.
\v 23 “Keima vang, nangho ding’a taopeh hi ka ngah’a, hichu Pakai douna-a kachonset louhel ding ahi. Chule thilpha le thildih nabol jing diuhi nangma kahil jing ding ahi.
\v 24 Ahinlah hiche hi naboltei diu ahi, Pakai chu ging’un chule tahsan umtah in jen’un, chule nangho ding’a thilkidang abol jouse chu geldoh jing’un.
\v 25 Ahinlah na chonset jom jing uva ahileh, nangho le na lengpau kisumang ding ahi,” ati.
\c 13
\s1 Philistine Douna Gal Che Jom
\p 
\v 1 Saul leng’a ahungpan chun akum somthum alhingtai chule kum somli le ni sungin lengvai anapon ahi.
\v 2 Saul in Israel sepaiho lah a kon'in atumbeh in mi sangthum alheng doh in, mi sangni chu Micmash le Bethel molsanga umpin, sangkhat vangchu Saul chapa Jonathan toh Benjamin gam Gibeah khopi’ah aum un chule mipi amoh cheng chu a inlam cheh uva asoltan ahi.
\v 3 Hiche phat chomkhat jouvin, Geba ah Philistine sepai touho chu Jonathan in asat in ahile, Philistine te chu ajoutauve. Hijeh chun Saul in gamsung tin ah kelki sumkon amut in, chule hitin aseiye, “Hebrew mipi te, hiche hi ngai tem’un, Philistine te dounan thoudoh un,” ati.
\v 4 Israel mite jousen Saul in Philistine te chu Geba ngahmun khat abulu in asuhmang jeh in Philistine til’a sangin Israelte chu ahot tauve tithu ajahdoh phat un, Israel sepai apumpi chu Gilgal’a Saul kithopi dia kikhom khom din thupeh anei tauvin ahi.
\v 5 Chuin Philistine te chu Israel tetoh kisat dingin akigong un, asakol kangtalai’u sangthum, sakol touthem mihem sang gup akigong’un chule mipi galsat ding chu twikhangle kam'a neldi jat hellin atam’un ahi.
\v 6 Israel mite nochimto’a aum’u ahetdoh phat’un, mipi te chu atijauvin alungdong gam tauvin, songko ho’ah, hamboh lah ah, chule kotong dung ah akisel gam taove.
\s1 Saul Lengpa Thungailou Samuel In Apho
\p 
\v 7 Mi phabep Jordan vadung agalkai’un, Gad le Gilead gamsung ah akisellun ahi. Hiche kahlah a chun Saul Gilgal ah aum'e chule amite chu tijat in akihot hot jengun ahi.
\v 8 Saul in Samuel chu nisagi jen angah in, hiti chun Samuel in jong akitepna banga Gilgal’a ahung thei tahlou jeh in, mipite akithe cheh gam tauvin ahi. \x + \xo 13:8 \xt 1 Samuel 10:8\x*
\v 9 Chuin Saul in, “Govam thilto ho leh chamna thilto neihin choi pehun “atin ahi. Chule Saul ama tah in govam thilto ho lhandohna aneitan ahi.
\v 10 Saul in govam thilto lhandohna aboljou tah in, Samuel jong ahunglhungpaiyin, chuin Saul chun kimutopi a chibai boldin apotdoh in ahi.
\v 11 Hichun Samuel in, “Ipi bolla nahim?” tia adohle, Saul in jong adonbutin, “Nangla nikho kitep nabanga hung louva, mipi ho jouse keija konna akithe cheh uva, chule Philistine ten Micmash a akikhop khom’u kamu phatna kanabol ahitai,” ati.
\v 12 Hijeh a chu kasei ahi, “Tua hi Philistine te eiho dou dinga Gilgal’a kigosadem a um u ahitan, Pakai henga panpina jeng jong kanathum man lou ahitai, hiche jeh a chu govamna thilto kanabol ahtai,” ati.
\v 13 Hichun Samuel in adonbut in, “Nangoltave, nangman Pakaiyin nathupeh ho nanit tapoi, asei angai lechun Pakaiyin Israel te lenga imatih chan’a dinga natung jing ta dinga,” ati.
\v 14 “Ahinla, tua hi na lenggam kichaitei ding ahitai. Pakaiyin ama lungthim he mikhat ahol ahitai. Pakaiyin amite chunga vaihom ding hi, lhendohsa akoi ahitai. Ijeh inem iti leh nangin thupeh nanit tapoi,” ati. \x + \xo 13:14 \xt Act 13:22\x*
\v 15 Chuin Samuel in Gilgal adalhan ajotna ding’a akichetai. Adang hon vang asepaite kithopi dia che Saul nung ajuitauve. Hichun amaho Gilgal apat Benjamin gamsung’a Gibeah ah ache toutauve. Hichun Saul in asepaite ama nungjui ho chu avetoh in ahile pasal mi jagup tobang asimdohtai.
\v 16 Chuin Saul le achapa Jonathan chule amani toh umkhom miho chu Benamin gamsung’a Geba a chun aum tauve, ahinlah Philistine mihon Micmash a panmun asem’un ahi.
\v 17 Hichun Philistine te, mibulu ding loithum chun panmun'a kon chun ahung potdoh'un, loikhat chu Shual gam Oprah jotna lampi chu ajon’un,
\v 18 Chule loikhat chun lhumlam a um Beth-horon lam chu ajon un, chule loi khat chun Zeboim phaicham gamthip kingah na gamgichin lampi ajot’un ahi.
\v 19 Hichelai chun Israel gam pumpia chun thihkheng khatcha ana umpon ahi, ajeh chu Philistine ten achuti louva ahile Hebrew miten chemjam le tengcha kikhen get unte atiu ahi.
\v 20 Hijeh a chu Israel te chu amitakip langkon, aloukaina, aheichau chule atupheng’u, akhet hem nom uva ahile akheng dinga Philistine te henga chesuh ji ahiuve.
\v 21 Tupheng, langkon thih, thihka, tucha thihmol, heicha chang suh hemna man chu paisa khat tobangbep ahi.
\v 22 Chuti chun chuche nikhoa kon’in Saul le Jonathan toh kiloi miho khut’a chun chemjam le tengcha khat cha, Saul le achapa Jonathan tilou adang akimupon ahi.
\v 23 Philistine sepaihon ho chun Micmash lampi chang din achedoh un ahi.
\c 14
\s1 Jonathan Thilgon Hangsan
\p 
\v 1 Nikhat hi Jonathan in agal manchah polea pangpa kom'a, “Hungin Philistine sepaiho umna langa khun galkai hite,” ati. Ahinlah Jonathan in, ipi abol ding chu apa henga ana hetsah pon ahi.
\v 2 Phat chomkhat jouvin, Saul in mi jagup chu Gibeah khopi pamlanga Migron mun'a kolbuthei phung vella chun anakhom khom’in ahi.
\v 3 Saul miho lah a chu Ahijah chun thempu von ephod chu akivon in ahi. Ahijah chu Ichabod sopipa Ahituh chapa ahin, Ahituh chu Phinehas chapa, Shiloh’a um Eli chapa Pathen thempu tupa ahi. Joathan in Israel te ngahmun adalhai ti koiman ahetlou ahi.
\v 4 Philisitne te ngahmun lutna dia chu Jonathan in lampi jet le veiya songpi kochet chut khat gel aumin, songpi khatpa min chu Bozez ahin, khatjopa chu amin Seneh ahi.
\v 5 Sahlama a songpi khat aum in, khatjoh Micmash lhanglam a um, Geba lam angat gel ahi lhone.
\v 6 Hichun Jonathan in, “Hiche cheptan lou sepai ho ngahmun lah a khun cheuhite, Pakiyin eini eikithopeh tei lhon ding ahi, ajeh chu Pakai chu koiman atin jouthei loudi ahi, Aman gal eijosah teidiu ahi, lhomcha hijongleu hen ijotei diu ahi,” ati.
\v 7 Hichun gollhang agavon popan, “Ipi hile phante natipen chu boljengin, chule keima nakom'a kaumnai, nagellhuh bangin bol jengin,” tin adonbut in ahi.
\v 8 Jonathan in, “Achutile aphalheh’e, eini galut hitin, amaho gakimu sah hite,” ati.
\v 9 Ahinla ama hon, ‘Naum na lhonah dingden lhon’in achuti louva ahileh katha diu ahi atiuva ahile ikaltou louding,
\v 10 Ahinlah, ‘Hung kaltou lhonin kisat ute’ atiuva ahileh ikaltou lhon ding ahin, hichu Pakaiya konna melchihna khat hi ding ahin aman eikithopi lhon’a i-jo lhon ding ahi,” ati.
\v 11 Chuin Philistine ten amu phat un ahoh un, “Veuvin, Hebrew miho akosunga kon'in ahung potdoh tauve atiuve.”
\v 12 Chuin khopi ngah a umpa chun Jonathan ahin sam’in, “Hichea hungkal tou in, thil khat navetsah unge atiuve,” ati. Chuin Jonathan in agalvon popa jah ah, “Hungin hungkal touvin, Pathen’in eipanpi lhona ijotei lhon ding ahi!” ati.
\v 13 Chuin amanin akhut le akeng atholhonin akaltou lhon ahile, Philistine mite chu Jonathan masanga abokhuma asot lhah jengle, anung’ahung kaltou agalvon popan ana that-thuthu jengin ahi.
\v 14 Amanin, mi somni athat lhonin, atahsa u chu acre keh khat’a len sung ‘ah athethang lhone.
\v 15 Hiti chun gangtah in, Philistine te gamsung ho lahle camp jousea thusoh chu ahung kithang soh tan, loujaova mipi holah le mijouse lah a chun tijat na nasatah in aum tan, sepai hon ho leh thilchom ho jong ati akihot hot’un chule liingjong akihot’e.
\s1 Israelten Philistine Te Ajo-U
\p 
\v 16 Chuin Saul in Gibeah Benjamin gamlang agal-lang chu avet’a ahile Philistine mite simsenlou chu muntin gamtin'ah ajam cheh gam tauvin ahi.
\v 17 Saul in asepai te jah a thu apen, “Min kou unlang, koi koi um’a, koi koi umlou ham,” ati. Hitia chu akihol ule Jonathan le agal manchah popa aum tapon ahi.
\v 18 Chuin Saul chu Ahijah chunga alunghang in, “Pathen thingkong chu hilam’ah hin choiyun,” ati. Hiche nikhoa chu Ahijah chu thempu von’in akivon in Pathen thingkong chu Israelte masang’a aput ahi.
\v 19 Ahin Saul thempupa toh aki houlim sungse chun Philistine ngahmun sunga chun boina ahaginjep jep’in ahi. Hichun Saul in thempupa jah a, “Imacha akhohpoi chejom jingo hite,” ati.
\v 20 Chuin Saul le asepaite chu galmun'a ahin nokhum ule Philistine mite chu amaho leh amaho akithat to tauvin, boina le kihet khelna nasatah asoh tan ahi.
\v 21 Chule tumasang’a Hebrew mi Philistine mite lah a ana jamlut ho jong chu Saul, Jonathan le Israel lah a adang dang ho langa ahung kiheilut jong aumin ahi.
\v 22 Hiti chun, Ephraim molsanga ana kisel Israel te jouse chun Philistine te ajam tauve tithu ajah phat un, amaho jong chun galsat na a chun hatah in anung’u adel’in ahi.
\v 23 Chuti chun hiche nikho chun Pakaiyin ami Israel te ahuhdoh in chule gal kisat chu Beth-aven geijin gal akisat peh’un ahi.
\v 24 Hiche nikho chun Israel te chu alung genthei lheh un ahi, ajeh chu, “Saul in kamelma te phu kalah theina dingin, nilhah ahi kahsea an nea chu sapset changhen tia mipi chu akihahsel sah ahi.” Hijeh a chu sun nilhum keiya koima anne umlou ahi.
\v 25 Hijeh chun, ama hon gamlah lampia chu khoibel khat ana um amu vang’un koiman anepouvin ahi.
\v 26 Chuin khoiju chu mipi koima chan ana ne ngam pouvin ahi. Ajeh chu kihahsel na uchu akichat’u ahi.
\v 27 Ahinlah Jonathan in apa thupeh chu ana jahlou jeh’in, atenggol muh’in khoiphang khat agah sun in, agah tepma ahile, atha akido ma ma jengin ahi.
\v 28 Ahin mikhat in hichu ana mudoh in, “Napan mipi nasatah’a eigihsal uva, tunia nilhum masanga an-nea mi chu sapset changhen tia eigaosap jeh uva koiman ka neh lou u ahi, hijeh a chu mipi jong hung lhasam ah ahi,” ati.
\v 29 Chuin Jonathan in, “Kapan gamsung hi agenthei sah ahi. Hitobang thupeh chun eiho ma ma eisuhgenthei u ahi. Ven hiche khoiju chu themkhat katep jeh a kamit hi iti hunghah doh hitam?” ati.
\v 30 Mipi jonghin amelmateu thil achom nauva amuhou hi aning anopmin nomtah in nele phachom louding ham? Hijeh a chu eihon tuni geija Philistine te tamtah itha theilou-u hilouham? ati.
\v 31 Chule hiche ni chun Micmash a kipat Aijalon geijin Philistine te chu anung adel’un athat peh’un chule mipi chu alhasam lheh jeng tauvin ahi.
\v 32 Chuin mipi chu thil kichomho chunga achuvin, kelgoiho, bongchalho, bongnouho, chu tollhanga athat’un thisan pum chun aneuvin ahi.
\v 33 Mikhat in Saul jah a, “Mihon sa thisan pumin aneuvin Pakai dounan achonse tauve,” tin anasei doh peh un ahi. Chuin Saul in, “Nathilbol’u chu adihlou ahi, songtum lentah khat kihol’unlang kilih piuvin,” ati. \x + \xo 14:33 \xt Semtilbu 9:4; Thempu Dan 7:26,27; 17:10-14; 19:26; Danbu Ni Na 12:16,23; 15:23\x*
\v 34 Saul in aseibe kit’in, “Sepai ho lah a khun chelut unlang a gancha u, akelngoi u, akelcha u jong kaheng’ah hin choiyun. Hichelai mun'a hin that’unlang chule naneh masang’un athisan chu lhoh kang hel un, Asa le thisan nehkop jeh a Pathen dounan chon dauvin,” ati.
\v 35 Chuin Saul in, Pakaiya dingin maicham asemin, hiche maicham chu Saul in Pakaiya dinga maicham asem masat pentah ahi.
\v 36 Chuin Saul in amite kom'a, “Eihon janteng kitolsuh uhitin Philistine te nung del uhitin, khovah kah’in amaho chu thatgam uhitin chomgam u hite,” ati. Hichun mipi jong, “Pha nasah sah chu bol jengin,’ atiuve. Ahivangin Thempupan, “Pathen dong masaute,” ahinti.
\v 37 Chuin Saul in Pathen adonge “Philistine te nung kadal diu ham? Kajo nadiuva nei panpi diuham? Ahinlah hiche nichun Pathen'in adonbut tapoi.
\v 38 Chuin Saul in lamkaiho kom'a aseijin, “Adih lou khat aumtai! Galmi lamkai jouse hikom'a hungun. Tunia ipi suhkhel ineijum?
\p Kikhol uhite chonset hi hoilaiya umham? Hinkhol doh un.
\p 
\v 39 Ajeh chu Israel huhhing'a hingjing Pakai min'a kasei ahi, kachapa Jonathan chunga um ahijongleh ama jeng jong thon louhel ’a thitei tei ding ahi,” ati. Ahinla mipi ho jouse lah a konna ipia konna boiham ti koiman aseipoi.
\v 40 Chuin Saul in aseijin, “Nangho lang khat ah um unlang, kei le kachapa Jonathan lang khat ah um lhoninge,” ati. Chule mipiten Saul kom'a chun, “Phante tia nagel chu aphapen ahi,” ati.
\v 41 Chuin Saul atauvin, “Oh Pakai Israel te Pathen, koihi dih’a, koihi dihlou hitam neisei peh’un,’ ati. Hichun vang asan ule Jonathan le Saul lhendoh ahung hin, hijeh chun mipi te chu ahoidoh tai. \x + \xo 14:41 \xt Minbu 27:21; 1 Samuel 28:6\x*
\v 42 Chuin Saul in, “Tun vang sang kit uhitin kei le Jonathan kah’a dingin,” Tun Jonathan chu athemmon hung kilang doh tai.
\v 43 “Ipi nabolkhel ham nei sei peh in?” hiti chun Saul in Jonathan kom'a adongin ahi. “Khoiju themkhat kana tep ahi,” thi Jonathan akiphong doh’e. “Tenggol muh’a themcha khat bou, hichun thina asotheiye,” atipeh in ahi.
\v 44 Saul in “Henge Jonathan, nathi tei ding ahi! nathi loule kei neita ding ahi.” Tin aseiyin ahi.
\v 45 Ahin mipiten Saul kom'ah, “Jonathan in Israel dia gal lentah eijopeh u ahin, Jonathan hi thi ding ham?’ tin anadongui. Hichu ahi ding ahile, Pathen'in jadahen, hingjing Pakai min'a kaseiju ahi, aluchunga kon samjang khat jong lha louding ahi. Ajeh chu tunin Pathen toh atongkhom in ahi,” atiuvin. Hijeh chun mipiten Jonathan ahuhdoh’un, athisah tapouve.
\v 46 Saul chu Philistine te nung adel naova kon'in achetou tan chule Philistine te jong aumnau vah ache tauve.
\v 47 Chuti chun Saul in Israel mite chunga lengvai anapon, muntinna amelmate jouse, Moab, Ammon chate, Edom, Zobah lengho chule Philistine mite toh akidouvin akiheina lam jousea gal ajoupeh in ahi.
\v 48 Aman thil lentah Amalek mite asat’in, ajouvin, chule amaho chom gam'a miho khutna kon'in Israel te ahuhdoh in ahi.
\v 49 Tun Saul chapa te chu Jonathan, Ishui chule Melchishua ahiuvin, chule achanu teni
\p lah a apeng masa’nu min Merab ahin, chule aneonu min Michal ahi.
\p 
\v 50 Chule Saul inneipi min Ahinoam ahin, Ahimaaz chanu ahi. Chule ajanel gal lamkaipa min chu Abner ahin, Saul pangahpa Ner chapa ahi .
\v 51 Chule Kish chu Saul pa ahin, chule Abner pa Ner chu Abiel chapa ahi.
\v 52 Chule Saul nikholai sungse chun Philistine mite toh kidouna chu anasa lheh jengin ahi, Chuti chun Saul in mihatle mihangsan amupou pouva ahile amanin ama-a dingin akipui jengin ahi.
\c 15
\s1 Saul In Amalek Mite Asuhmang
\p 
\v 1 Nikhat Saul kom'a Samuel chun, “Israel te chunga leng dinga nangma thaonu dinga eina sol’a chu Pakai ama tah chu ahi, hijeh a chu tua Pakai thusei hi nangai ding ahi,” ati. \x + \xo 15:1 \xt 1 Samuel 10:1\x*
\v 2 Hiche hi van gam sepaite Pakaiyin aphondoh ahi, Israel mite Egypt a konna ahung potdoh uva chu lampia iti analamtin jeh uva, Amalek chunga hi talen kamatsah ding ahitai. \x + \xo 15:2 \xt Potdohbu 17:8-14; Danbu Ni Na 25:17-19\x*
\v 3 Tun che unlang Amalek mite chu abonchan gathat gamkeijun, nao noichep ho geija natha ding’u, khatcha jong nakhen lou diu, pasal, numei, chapang, naosen, bong, kelcha, sangongsao, chule sangan ho chang geiya natha gam diu ahi,” ati.
\v 4 Chutah in Saul in mipi ho chu Telaim mun’ah akhomin, amaho chu Israel mite’a kon'in keng sepai sang jani chule Judah a konna mi sangsom ahiuve.
\v 5 Chuin Saul le a sepaite chu Amalek te khopi’ah alut un, phaicham mun khat’ah chun angah tauve.
\v 6 Saul in Ken mite ho gihna thu apen, “Amalek miho umna-a kon'in potdoh’un, achuti louva ahile Amalek mihotoh nathitha dingu ahi, Nangho vang chu kami Israel chate jouse Egypt’a konna ahung potdoh uchun hepina namusah un ahi,” tin thu apen ahi. Chuin Ken mihon apot akigot’un adalha tauve.
\v 7 Chuin Saul in Amalek mite chu Havilah apat solam Egypt toh kigalsai Shur khopi lutna geijin gal ana sat’in asumangpeh tan ahi.
\v 8 Chuin aman Amalek lengpa chu ahingin aman in midang jouse chu chemjam in athat soh hel tan ahi.
\v 9 Ahinlah Saul le mipi chun, Amalek mi Agag le kelngoi, kelcha, bongchal thao ho leh ahoipen ho ahing hoijun, aphalou ahoilou chengse chu asumanghel tan ahi.
\s1 Pathen In Saul Leng Dia Apai
\p 
\v 10 Chuin Pakaiyin Samuel kom'ah aseijin ahi,
\v 11 “Saul lenga kana tun hi kakisihtai ajeh chu aman eidonse tapon chule kathupeh ho jong anit tapoi,” ati. Hiche thu Samuel in ajahdoh phat in alung atongkhan, jan khovah hellin Pakai hengah akaptai.
\v 12 Ajing jingkah matah in Samuel jong Saul kimupi dingin achetan ahile, mi khat’in, “Saul chun Carmel khopi’a ama le ama kihet jingna ding mangmo khat akisem din Gilgal lam achesuh tan ahi,” tin aseipeh tan ahi.
\v 13 Chuin Samuel in Saul chu amu phat in, Saul in kipah tah in ana salam, “Pakaiyin phatthei naboh hen, keiman Pakai seibang bangin kaboltai,” atin ahi.
\v 14 Samuel in, “Ahile kanabeng’a kelngoi hamgin le bongchal hamgin kajah hi ipiba hija ong?” ati.
\v 15 Hichun Saul in adonbut in, “Adih’e, kasepai te hon ama le Amalek mite a konna ahin kaiju ahi, ajeh chu mipi hon kelngoi ho leh bongchal aphapen penho chu, ‘Pakai na Pathen lhaina dinga ahing hoiju ahi,’ adang ho vang kasumang heltaove,” ati.
\v 16 Chuin Samuel’in Saul kom'a aseiyin, “Thip in! Tujan Pakaiyin kahenga thu asei hi ngaijin!” ati. Hichun Saul in, “Ipi naseipeh em?” tin Saul in adongin ahi.
\v 17 Chuin Samuel in, “Nangma neocha nakigel maithei ahi, nangma Israel nam mite jouse lah a lamkai nahi hilou ham? Pakaiyin leng dinga thaonanu ahi.
\v 18 Chule Pakaiyin anatong dinga nasolla, chen michonse Amalek mite gathat gamkeijin atin.
\v 19 Ipi bolla Pakai thupeh nanit louham? Ipi jeh pentah jeh a thil nachom’a Pakai mitmua thilse nabol ham?” ati.
\v 20 Saul’in, “Ahinlah Pakai thupeh kabolle, bollin tia eisol na kagabolle. Agag lengpa bou ahing’a kahin kai ahin. Ahin adangse vang kahin that gamnai,” ati nalaiyin ahi.
\v 21 Chutengleh kasepaiten, kelngoi, kelcha, bongchal, athaolai, ahoilai ho leh thil kichom ho hi Gilgal’a na Pathen houna-a dinga ahin kaiyu ahi bouve,” ati.
\v 22 Ahin Samuel in, “Pakai chu pumgo thilto kibol le athupeh ngaipeh hi hoijoh’a hi kipah inte natim? Ngaijin! Sei ngai kiti hi gan kilhai sanga phajo ahin, kangcha athusei ngaipeh kiti hi kelngoichal thao sang’a phajo ahi,” tin adonbut in ahi.
\v 23 Pakai doumah kibol kiti hi kithoi phunsan tobang ahin, chule louchal kiti hi doi houva themmo chan tobang ahi. Pakai thupeh napai jeh a Aman leng nahina’a konna napai ahitai,” ati.
\s1 Saul In Ngaidam Athum
\p 
\v 24 Saul in, “Henge, keima kachonsetai, keiman neihilna ho jong kangaipon chule Pakai thupeh jong kanit tapoi, kasepaite kagin jeh a athil thum hou kabolpeh ahitai,” ati.
\v 25 “Hijeh chun kachonsetna ho hi nei ngaidam inlang chule Pathen kahou theina din nei kinung lhonpin,” ati.
\v 26 Ahinlah Samuel in adonbut in, “Keitoh ikinung lhon theilou ding ahi! Pakai thupeh na paimang jeh a, aman Israel te lenga konna napaidoh ahitai,” ati.
\v 27 Hichun Samuel chemang dinga akiheiya ahile, aman asangkhol chol mong chun aman in aloi eh-lotan ahi. \x + \xo 15:27 \xt 1 Samuel 28:17; 1 Lgt 11:30,31\x*
\v 28 Chuin Samuel in ajah ah, “Tunia hi Pakaiyin Israel te lenggam chu nanga konna nalahpeh’a, nang sanga phajo khat apeh doh ahitai,” ati.
\v 29 “Israel Pathen lal loupi tah chun ajou louding, alung jong khel louding ahi, ajeh chu ama lungkhel ding mihem tobang ahipoi,” ati
\v 30 Hichun Saul’in ngaidam athum kit in, “Chonse kahi, keiman kakihet e, ahin nei lungset in, kalamkai ho masang le, kami Israel mite masanga kajum lou nadin, nei kilhonpi tei teijin, chutile Pakai na Pathen kahou ding ahi,” ati.
\v 31 Hichun Samuel jong achaina in kinung lhonpi ding anomtai, chule Pathen houna ah ajaotai.
\s1 Samuel In Agag Lengpa Atha
\p 
\v 32 Chuin Samuel in, “Agag lengpa chu kaheng’a hinpuijun,” atin ahile, Agag lengpa jong kinemtah in akipah lheh in ahi, ajeh chu ama alunggel’a chu, “kagim na ho kichaiya, eikilhadoh di ahitai,” tia agel ahi.
\v 33 Ahinlah Samuel in, “Na chemjam’a hi minu acha pasal tamtah nana that in, tun nanu jong hitobanga chu chaneilou hitahen,” atin ahi. Chuin Samuel in Agag chu Pakai masang ah Gilgal mun ah asatchen chen tan ahi.
\v 34 Chuin Samuel Ramah a ainlam ajon in chule Saul jong Gibeah a ain’ah akile tai.
\v 35 Chujou kalsen Samuel in Saul kimupin ache kha-ngai tapoi, ahinlah tanglou vin alunghempi jingin ahi. Pakaiyin Saul Israel te lenga anatun chu akisih lheh jenge.
\c 16
\s1 Samuel In David Leng Dia Thao Anu
\p 
\v 1 Pakaiyin Samuel kom'a, “Nangman phat sottah Saul chung changa pul nadou chu phaset tante, keiman ama chu Israel te leng ahina a konna kapaidoh ahitai, hijeh chun nathao theiyah olive tao kithun dim inlang Bethlehem’ah chetan. Hiche khopi cheng amin Jesse kitipa chu holdoh in, ajeh chu keiman achate lah a khat chu leng dinga kalhendohsa hitai,” ati.
\v 2 Ahin Samuel in adongin, “Keiman hichu iti kabolthei ding ham? Hichepi chu Saul in jadoh henlang hileh eitha loding ahi,” ati. Pakaiyin adonbut in, “Bong ala khat kikai inlang chen, chule Pakaiya dinga gan kilhaina-a dinga hung kahi tin,” ati.
\v 3 “Chule gan kilhaina ah Jesse kouvin, chuteng keiman achate lah a koipen chu kei dinga thao nanuding ham ti chu nahetsah nange,” ati.
\v 4 Chuin Samuel in Pakaiyin ahilbang chun aboltai. Ama Bethlehem alhun phat chun, khopi sunga um upaho jouse chu kitihotpum pum’in akimu piuvin, “Ipi adihlou umham? Chamna puma nahungu hinam?” tin ana dongun ahi.
\v 5 Hichun Samuel in, “Henge, keima gan kilhaina a dinga hunga kahi, na boncha uvin Pakaiya dingin kisutheng unlang gankilhaina’a dingin cheuhite,” tin Samuel in adonbut’in ahi. Chuin Samuel in Jesse le achate akou khom’in kisuhthengna kin agong’in, chule pumgo thilto a jong ajao diuvin atem in ahi.
\v 6 Chuin amaho chu ahunglhun phat’un, aman Eliab chu khatvei aven chule alungthim ah, “Pakaiyin alhendohpa hitei yinte!” tin agel’e
\v 7 Ahinlah Pakaiyin Samuel kom'a aseiyin, “Nangman atahsapoh ahilou le asandan chun vehih-in, ajeh chu keiman ama chu kadeilou ahi, ijeh inem itileh Pakaiyin mihem thilvet bang avet ahipoi, ajeh chu mihem’in apolam melput avet ahin, Pakaiyin vang alungsung avet ahi,” ati.
\v 8 Chuin Jesse in achapa Abinadab chu Samuel anaijep’a amasang’a ding din asollin ahilah Samuel in, “Ama jong hi Pakai lhendohsa chu ahipoi,” ati.
\v 9 Aban’in Jesse in Shimea ahin koudoh in, ahinlah Samuel in, “Ama jong hi Pakaiyin alhendoh chu ahipoi,” ati.
\v 10 Chuti chun Jesse chate sagi jen chu Samuel angsung’ah ahinpuilut in, ahin Samuel in Jesse adongin, “Pakaiyin hiche ho hi khatcha alhengpoi,” ati.
\v 11 Chuin Samuel in Jesse jah a, “Nachate hichang bou hi hitam?” tia adohle, aman jong, “Aneopen khat aum nalaiye, ahinlah ama hi in’ah aumpoi, loujaova kelngoi le kelcha ho aching’e,” tin adonbut in ahile Samuel in, “Ama chu gakou sah’un, ama chu ahung lhun tokah’a, toujong i-tou loudiu chule anneh twidon jong ibol loudiu ahi,” ati.
\v 12 Hiti chun Jesse in akou ding mi asollin ahi. Ama chu mi tahsa phatah chule amit-ha hoitah ahi. Chuin Pakaiyin, “Thao nuding chu ama hi ahi,” ati.
\v 13 David asopi te ho lah a kon'in ahung dingdoh’in, hichun Samuel’in olive thao alan thao chu anu tai. Hiche nia kipan chun Pakai Lhagao chu thaneitah in David chung’ah ahungchu tan ahi. Chuin Samuel Ramah ah akile tai.
\s1 David In Saul Thutanna'a Na Atoh
\p 
\v 14 Hiti chun Pakai lhagaovin Saul adalhatan ahi, chule Pakaiyin ahinsol lhagao engse khat’in Saul chu lunggimna le tijatnan abolgim lheh jengin ahi.
\v 15 Saul asohte ho lah a phabep khat in akom'ah, “Tua hi Pathen a konna lhagao gilou khat in nasuhgim ahi kaheuve,” atiuve.
\v 16 “Hijeh chun, kapu, neisol’unlang semjang saithem khat gahol unge. Hitia lhagao engsen nahin phah phat phat le ama chun semjang saiyin tin, chuteng damdoh kitji tan nate,” atiuve.
\v 17 Hichun Saul in, “Apha lheh jenge, cheuvinlang semjang saithem tah mikhat gahol unlang, chule ama chu kahenga hin puijun,” ati.
\v 18 Chuin asohte ho lah a mi khat in Saul jah ah, “Jesse chapa te ho lah a khat, Bethlehem mi, semjang saithem tah, hiche goh chu hilouva mihangsan, gal-hat, galbolmi, ijakai hekhen themtah, chule mel-hoitah, chujongleh Pakaiyin aumpi mi ahi,” ati.
\v 19 Chuin Saul in thupolea mikhat Jesse henga thulhut ding’in asollin, “Nachapa David kelngoiching chu neihinsol peh in,” ati.
\v 20 Saul in David athum chu Jesse in anop peh’in, changlhah toh, lengpitwi haikhat, chule kelnou khat, sangan khat apohsah in ahi.
\v 21 Chuin David Saul kom’ah achen, Saul chu ajen pan tan ahi, Saul in David angailu lheh jengin chule David chu Saul galvonpon apang tai.
\v 22 Chuin Saul in Jesse kom'a thu athot in, “Lungset tah in David hi kakom'ah kakin bol in pang jeng ta hen, ajeh chu achung’a kalung alhailheh jengin ahi,” ati.
\v 23 Chule Pathen'in ahinsol lhagao engse chun Saul ahinphah tengleh, David in semjang chu asaipeh ji teng, Saul chu ahung limdohjin chule lhagao engse chun adalhaji in ahi.
\c 17
\s1 Goliath In Israel te Achou
\p 
\v 1 Judah gamsung Socoh mun'a chun Philistine mite galsat dingin akikhom’un, chule Socoh le Azekah kikah’a Ephes-dammim’a chun ngahmun asem tauvin ahi.
\v 2 Chuin Saul le Israel te jong akikhom’un, Philistine te dounan Elah phaicham panga ngahmun akisem’un ahi.
\v 3 Philistine te chu lhangkhat ah akigol’un chule Israel te jong chu lhangkhat ah akigol’un chule akikah uva phaicham khat in akhentan un ahi.
\v 4 Chule Philistine te mihat tah Gath khopia a konna hungkon, amin Goliath kitipa chun Israel te satdingin Philistine te ngahmun a kon'in ahung potdoh'in ahi. Ama chu tong gup le khap khat jen in asangin ahi.
\v 5 Chule aman sum-eng lukhuh akhuh in, sum-eng a kisem ompho shekel sang nga jen agih aki-ah in ahi.
\v 6 Akengte ni jong sum-eng’a kitomjol ahin, chule alengkouva ama sum-eng tengcha akipoh chu kitungdoh peh ahi.
\v 7 Atengcha lung tumbi tejen ahin, atengpeh jong thih jeng, gihdan chu shekel jagup’a gih ahin, apho chu mikhat poh ahi.
\v 8 Goliath adingin Israel galsat miho jah a ahin samin, “Ipi dinga galsat dinga hung kigola nahiuvem, keima Philistine mihatpa kahin, nangho Saul sohte mai mai nahiuve, ei kisatpi ding mikhat hung kilheng doh un,” atin ahi.
\v 9 “Aman keima eitha le nasoh’u kahi diu, ken ama katha le keiho soh nahi diu ahi,” ati.
\v 10 “Tunia hi Israel galsatho kachou nahiuve, kakisatpi ding pa chu hin soldoh’un,” ati.
\v 11 Chuin Saul le Israel mite jousen Plilistine mipa thusei ajah phat’un, akichalheh jeng tauvin ahi.
\s1 Jesse In David Saul Ngahmun’a Asol
\p 
\v 12 David kitipa chu Judah gam Bethlehem khopia Ephrah mi Jesse chapa ahin, hiche lai chun Jesse chu ateh lheh jeng tan chule aman chapa get jen aneiyin ahi.
\v 13 Jesse chapa alen thumho, chu Eliab, Abindab, chule Shimea ho chu Philistine te sat dia Saul lengpa sepai a pang ahiuve.
\v 14 David chu achate lah a aneopen ahi. David ute thum ho chu Saul sepaiho toh khom’a ahiuve.
\v 15 Ahin David chu Saul inpia konna apa kelngoi chin kithopi dia Bethlehem ah hung kile kitji jia ahi.
\v 16 Ni somli sungin jingkah, nilhah seh leh Philitine mihatpan Israel sepai ho ahin naiyin achou jingin ahi.
\v 17 Nikhat Jesse in David jah ah, “Hiche pucha-a chang kanpoh hile changlhah lhon som hi choijin lang gangtah in naute gapen.
\v 18 Chule hiche bongnoiha-a kisem lhon som hi sepaiho lamkaipa pen. Na-ute iti nauvem gavenlang, thu nahin nungpoh kit ding ahi,” tin anasollin ahi.
\v 19 David ute ho chu Saul to umkhom'a ahiuvin, Israel sepaiho chu Elah phaichama gal mun’ah um ahiuve.
\v 20 Chuin David in akelngoiho chu avetup din mi khat angansen, jingkah matah in apan athupeh banginthilho chu apon, achen ahile sepaiho galsat dinga ngahmun dalha dinga akigotuva a-ao laitah’un ngahmun chu agalhungin ahi.
\v 21 Israel te le Philistine sepaiho galkisat dia kidinte-a kimaitoa akigol laitah’un,
\v 22 David in thilkeo chingtup pa henga athilpoh ho chu adalhan, gangtah in a-ute ho chibai agaboltai.
\v 23 Aman a-ute ho akihoulimpi laitah in, Gath mi Philistine mihatpa chu Philistine sepai ho lah a kon'in ahung potdoh'in ana seingaiji banginasamin, Israel mite chu ahin choukit tan ahile, hichu David in ajatan ahi.
\v 24 Chuin Israel sepaiten hiche mipa chu amu phat’un akicha behseh jengun ajam tauvin ahi.
\v 25 Hichun alah uva mikhat in David jah a, “Hiche mihatpa chu namu em? Aniseh leh hitia khu hung potdoh’a Israel sepaite achou chou jin ahi, koi hileh ama thatpen pen khu lengpan kipaman lentah apeh ding, achanu khat jong aji ding’a apeh ding, chule Israel ten kai peh dingdol a kon'in jong onthol sah ding ahi,” ati.
\v 26 David in akimvella ding Israel sepai ho jah ah, “Hiche cheptanlou Philistine mahatpa that’a, Israel mite avettomna konna huhdoh mi chu ipi amu ding ham? Ipi hile iti hiche cheptanlou Philistine pan hingjing Pathen sepaite ajumso ding ham?” ati.
\v 27 Chuin miho chun adonbut un, “Henge hiche mipa that pen pen chu kipaman akisei chu peh ding ahi,” atiuve.
\v 28 Ahinlah David ute ho lah a alenpen Eliab chun David thusei ajahdoh phat’in alung ahang in, “Hichea hi ipi nahung bolle ham? Na kelngoi hon ho chu ipi itihen nati ham? Nakiletsahna le na jonchih na chu kahe nai, hichea kidounaho venom mai maija hunga nahi bouve,” ati.
\v 29 Hichun David in, “Ken ipi kabol em? Thudoh kagah nei mai mai ahi,” tin adonbut in ahi.
\v 30 Chuin amahoa kon'in adang ho langah akihei kit in athudoh mama adoh’a ahile, ama hon jong aseima ma asei kit un ahi.
\v 31 David thudoh chu Saul lengpa kom agalhut un ahile Saul lengpan jong aheng’a ahin pui diuvin thu ape tan ahi.
\s1 David In Goliath Atha
\p 
\v 32 “Hiche Philistine mipa chunga khun boi tahih’un, kache ding kaga kimaitopi ding ahi,” tin David in Saul jah a aseiyin ahi.
\v 33 Saul in, “Angol nahim! nangman hiche Philistine mihatpa nasatna najo nading lampi aum theipoi, nangma chapang chabou nahin, ama akhangdon laiya kipatna galsat mi ahi,” ati.
\v 34 Ahinlah David in, “Kapa kelngoi ho leh kelcha ho jong kana vetkol ahin, nasohpa hin apa kelngoi anachin na’a chun keipi bahkai le vompi ahunga kelnou ho ahung lhohmang ding agot tengleh,
\v 35 Anung kadellin, kakidalpin, akamsung’a kon'in kahuhdohjin ahi, chule keima thadia eigot tengleh, akha ah kaman in kathat jitai.
\v 36 Keipi le vompi ani nia hitia chu kabolji ahin chule tua jong Philistine cheptan loupa jong chutia chu kabol ding ahi, ajeh chu aman hingjing Pathen sepai ho ajumso jeh a hitia chu bolding ahi.
\v 37 Pakaiyin keipi bahkai le vompi khutphanga konna eihuhdoh pa chun tunia jong hiche Philistine mihatpa a konna eihuhdoh tei ding ahi, ” atin boltei agoi. Hichun Saul in achaina a lunggel lhahna aneiyin, “Aphai nakigot bang chun boltan chule Pakaiyin naumpi jingta hen,” ati.
\v 38 Chuin Saul in David agalvon apen, alukhuh sum-eng a kisem akhuhpeh in, thih sangkhol a-ahpeh tan ahi.
\v 39 Hichun David in agalvon chunga chun achemjam ako’in, kal khat kal agah son le galvon ho akivon khahlou jeh in, achethei tapon ahi. Hijeh chun aman Saul jah a, “Hiche ho pumin chethei ponge, ajeh chu hiche ho hi kamang theipoi,” atin, asut lhatai.
\v 40 Hichun David in vadung songchang jolsel chang nga akilopan, akelngoi chinna sakhao neovah akikon, chuin akelngoi chinna tenggol le sailungchang kapna gophel akichoijin, Philistine mihatpa umna phaicham ajontai.
\v 41 Goliath jong ahung potdoh'in David lam ahin jontai chule agalvon popa chu ahung masan ahi.
\v 42 Goliath in David chu phatah a avettoh phat’in, chapang mel-hoi cha bou ahinah laijeh in, asit behseh jeh in alung ahang tai.
\v 43 David jah a lunghang tah in, “Keima uicha kahim? Mol kichoija kahenga hung nahim?” ati. Hichun Philistine mipa chun, apathen ho min pan in David chu agaosap tai.
\v 44 Goliath in David chu achouvin, “Hilam ah hungin, keiman natahsa chu vachate le gamsa te kapeh ding ahi,” ati ahi.
\v 45 David in Philistine mipa chu adonbut in, “Nangma chemjamle tengcha choiya hung nahin, Ahinlah keima vang van gam sepai galsat te Pakai min'a hung kahi.
\v 46 Tunia hi Pakaiyin najo ding, keiman nang katha-a nalu katan ding, natahsa thisa chu vachate le gamsate kapeh ding chule leiset pumpin Israel Pathen khat aum'e ti ahet diu ahi,” ati.
\v 47 “Chule hichea hung kikhom jousen Pakaiyin chemjam le tengchan ahuhhingpoi ti ahet dingu ahi. Ajeh chu galsat hi Pakaiya ahin, aman nangho kakhutna eipeh doh diu ahitai,” ati.
\v 48 Goliath ahung kipatdoh a David henglam ahin jot phat in, David chu kintah in Philistine mihatpa toh kisuto dingin alhaisuh tan ahi.
\v 49 David in akhut in asakhao sung asoh in, song chang khat aladoh in, ah-songse’a chu asea ahile, Philistine mipa chalpang ah achun, songchang chu alut in, Goliath tol-lhang ah alhutan ahi.
\v 50 Chuti chun David in chemjam pang louhellin, songchang khat seh le ah-songse in Goliath ajoutan ahi. \x + \xo 17:50 \xt 2 Samuel 21:19\x*
\s1 Israel ten Philistine Mite Adelkhum’u
\p 
\v 51 Chuin David in adel lut paiyin, Goliath chemjam chu asatdoh in, ama chemjam ma ma chun alol atantan ahi. Chuin Philistine mipiten ami hatpa’u athi amu phat un, akinung heijun ajam tauvin ahi. \x + \xo 17:51 \xt 2 Samuel 21:19\x*
\v 52 Chuin Israel te le Judah miho akipat’un, a-aovun, phaicham le Ekron kotpi aphah kah seuvin Philistine mite nung adel’un ahi. Chule Philistine mipi ho chu Shaariam lam lhon lhungin thilong akijam thang’un, Gath le Ekron chan geijin athilong u chu alum thang sohkei jenginn ahi.
\v 53 Chuin Israel chaten Philistine mite anungdel uva kon'in ahung kinung leuvin, angahun hou chu asumang’un achom tauvin ahi.
\v 54 Chuin David in Philistine mihatpa luchang chu alan Jerusalem ah ahin potai; ahin galvon vang apon in’ah akoitai.
\v 55 David Philistine pa satdinga akon doh chun Saul in agalvon popa Abner jah ah, “Hiche gollhang pa khu koicha ham? tin adongin ahile Abner in jong, “Atahbah in kahepoi,” tin anadonbut e.
\v 56 Hichun lengpan jong, “Aphai, koiham hinkhol chen’in,” ati.
\v 57 David in Goliath ahintha jouva ahung lhun in, Abner in Philistine mihatpa luchang chu Saul kom'ah ahin lhuttan ahi.
\v 58 Hichun Saul in, “Gollhang, napa koiham neisei peh in,” atin ahile David in adonbut in, “Kapa min Jesse ahin, Bethlehem a um kahiuve,” ati.
\c 18
\s1 Saul David Chung’a Athangthip
\p 
\v 1 David in Saul akihoupi jouvin, lengpa chapa Jonathan toh akimuton, Jonathan in David angailut jeh chun, akikah lhona kintah’a kitepna khat semdin akigong lhontan ahi.
\v 2 Hichenia kipat chun Saul in David akom'ah akikoi jingtan ainlamah akilesah kit tapon ahi.
\v 3 Jonathan in David chu adei behseh jeh le ama akingailut banga angailut jeh in a-itih a kikhenpi lou dingin, akikah lhon-ah kihahsel na khat asemin ahi.
\v 4 Jonathan in hiche akihahsel na melchihnan, achunga kai asangkhol chol chu asut lhan asilpeh in, chule avonho, achemjam le athalpi chule akonggah geiyin David apetan ahi.
\v 5 Chuti chun Saul in David chu asolna lam lamah achejin alolhing sohkeiyin ahi. Hijeh chun Saul in asepaiho chunga gallamkai dingin atungin ahile, mijouse jong achung ah akipah cheh-un ahi.
\v 6 Israel miten galjona ahin neijouvun inlama ahung kile kit-un, David in Philistine te ahintha jouvun, khopi jousea nupiho ahung potdoh’un, Saul lengpa ahung kimupiuvin ahi, numeihon khongcha le tumgingthei toh thon kipahtah in lampumin la asauvin ahi.
\v 7 Vailhun na’a alasah’u chu hiche ahi, “Saul in asang asangin athat in, David in asangsomasangsom in athat’e!” tin alachoiyun ahi. \x + \xo 18:7 \xt 1 Samuel 21:11; 29:5\x*
\v 8 Hiche chun Saul nasatah in alunghan sah in, “Hiche hi ipiham? ama hon David achoisangun, sangsom athat’e atiuvin, kei sangkhat that in eiseijun. Abankit tengleh lengin hin kitun kit taveh tao!” atin ahi.
\v 9 Hijeh chun, hichenia kipat chun, Saul in David chu thangthipna mitvet in avepan tan ahi.
\v 10 Ajing nikho maman Pathen a kon'in lhagao phalou Saul chungah ahung chukitin, insunga angol pen bangin apengin ahile, David in nidanga bangin, akhut in semjang asaijin ahi. Ahin Saul in akhut’ah tengcha akichoijin ahi.
\v 11 Chule hetmanlouvin, tengchan David chu akhon ahi, bangtoh khobeh ding agot ahin, ahinlah David in ana otdoh in ahi.
\v 12 Pathen'in Saul adlhah’a David aumpi jeh chun Saul in Daivd chu akichalheh jengtan ahi.
\v 13 Hijeh chun Saul in, David chu sepai sangkhat chung’a lamkai dingin akoiyin gamla tah in asolmang tan ahi. David in jong kitup tah in alamkaijin gal akonpi in ahi.
\v 14 Chuin David Pakaiyin aumpi jeh chun imalam jouse’ah alolhing lheh jingin ahi.
\v 15 David lolhing nathu te ho Saul in ajahdoh kit phat in, akicha cheh cheh jengtan ahi.
\v 16 David in nasatah’a, kituptah’a gal alamkai jeh in, Israel te jouse le Judah nam mite jousen jong David chu angailu un, akipapi lheh jengun ahi.
\s1 David In Saul Chanu Akichenpi
\p 
\v 17 Nikhat hi Saul in David kom'ah, “Kachanu alenjo nu Merab khu naji dia pedinga kigongsa kahi. Ahinlah amasan nangma Pakaiya dinga gal hang mong nahi photchenna neipen,” ati. Ajeh chu Saul’in alunggel’ah, “Keima tah in katha sangin, Philistine tetoh kidou dingin kisol henlang hinthat doh-uleh,” tia angaito ahi.
\v 18 David in, “Kei koi kahiya chule ka insung mite hi Israel a ipi hiya, keima lengpa tupa kahi ding ham? Chule kappa insung mite jong ima ahipoi” ati.
\v 19 Hijeh chun, Merab toh akichen nading phat ahung lhun phat in, Saul in, Adriel kiti Meholath mipi toh Merab chu akichensah tan ahi.
\v 20 Ahinlah Saul chanu Michal chu David to akidei lhonin, hichu Saul in ajahdoh phat in akipah lheh jengin ahi.
\v 21 Hichun Saul in alunggel in, “Hiche Philistine te khutna athina dinga phat kijen chomkhat ahi,” atin ahinlah Saul anivei nan David kom'a chun, “Katupa nahi tei ding tai,” ati.
\v 22 Saul in avaipote kom'a chun, David jah a aseidiu thu apen, “Lengpan nadei lheh jenge, chule keiho jong pha kasalheh jeng uve, hijeh chun lengpa tupa nahi ding pha nasah louham?” tia aseipeh din ahil’e.
\v 23 Saul avaipoten hiche thu ho chu David kom'a aseijun ahile, David in, “Kei mivaicha, insung lhasam le mi nahsahmo, lengpa tupa-a iti kapan thei ding ham? Tin anadonbut in ahi.
\v 24 Chuin Saul mite hon hiche thu chu Saul kom'a asei doh phat un.
\v 25 Saul in David kom'a asei diu ahil kit’in, “Lengpan moulah man dia adei chu ahile amelmate chunga phulah nadinga Philistine te chep jakhat tilou adang imacha angeh poi tin seipeh un,” ati. Ahinla Saul chun David chu Philisine te khutna thisah tei agot ahi.
\v 26 Saul lengpa thil ngeh chu David in ajahdoh phat in kipahtah in asangtai, anikho kitep alhun masang'in,
\v 27 David ama le amite akipatdoh un, Philistine te mi jani agathat’un ahi. Hiti chun David in lengpan angaichat chu asuh bulhit peh in, chep kitan chu agapetan ahi. Chuin Saul in achanu Michal chu David ji dingin apetan ahi.
\v 28 Pakaiyin David aumpi ti kichen tah in ahetan, chule achanu Michal angailut dan ahetan ahi.
\v 29 Saul in David chu agingcheh cheh jengtan, hijeh chun Saul chu ahinkho lhumkeiyin David din amelma ahijom jing jengtai.
\v 30 Philistine te sepaiten aphatseh leh ahin nokhum jing jengun, ahin David hatna achang jing jengin, David min nasatah in akithang tan ahi.
\c 19
\s1 Saul In David Tha Ding Agot
\p 
\v 1 Saul in achapa Jonathan le asohte ho jouse toh David thana ding lunggel anei khompi tan ahi. Ahinlah Joanthan le David golphatah ahi lhon jeh chun,
\v 2 Jonathn in David jah a, “Kapan, jing jingkah le tha ding nagoi, chinghtheiyin, loulai sunga kisel nading mun khat kihol’in,” tin apa thilgon ho jouse chu aseipeh tan ahi.
\v 3 “Chutengleh, keiman kappa chu munchom khatna puidong ing kating, nachung chang thu kihoulimpi ing katin, kamudoh chengse chu nang ka seipeh ding nahi,” tin aseipeh kit tan ahi.
\v 4 Ajing jingkah in, Jonathan in David chung chang thu apa kom'ah aphatna le athilpha boljeng aseipeh in ahi. Chule Jonathan in apa kom'a chun, “Lengpa chu asoh David douna-a chonse louding ahi chule David in nangma dounan thil imacha abolpoi, aman ajochanin aphat jousen nakithopin ahi,” ati.
\v 5 “Pathen thahatna jal'a Philistine mihatpa anatha-a Israel te dinga gal lentah eina jopeh-u phatlai chu nasuhmil hitam? Hichea thilsoh chung changa chu nangma nana kipa dehset hilou ham? Achutia ahileh imacha bolselou, mona neilou David chu ipi bolla thading nagot ham? Ajeh imacha aumpoi!” ati.
\v 6 Hijeh chun Saul in Jonathan thusei chu phatah in angaijin chuin akihahsel’in, “Hingjing Pakai min pan’a kasei ahi, David chu kithat louding ahi,” ati
\v 7 Hiche jouchun Jonathan in David akouvin, thil ijakai asepeh tan ahi. Chule aman David chu Saul kom'ah apuijin, amasa bangin David in leng inpi’ah na atong kit in ahi.
\v 8 Chuin Philistine tetoh gal kisatna aumkit in, David in asepaite akipuijin Philistine tetoh akisat in, amaho nasatah in athat-in ahile, amaho ajam tauve.
\v 9 Ahinlah nikhat hi Saul in’ah atouvin tengcha akhut ah akichoijin ahile, Pathen a konna hungkon lhagao dihlou chun hetman louvin achungah ahung chu kit’in ahile, David in angai bangin semjang asailaitah in,
\v 10 Saul in David chu atengcha choiya chun akhoa, bangtoh khobeh ding agotna ahile, David ana ki-otdoh in, atengcha chun bang ah akibut lut jengin, hiche jan chun David akiseldoh tan ahi.
\s1 Michal In Daivd Hinkho Ahuhdoh
\p 
\v 11 Chuin Saul in David ain-langa avelhi dingin asepaite asollin ahi. Asepaite jah ah, ajing jingkah teng aina konna ahung potdoh tengleh natha dingu ahi, tin thu apen ahi. Ahinlah ainneipi Michal in David jah a, “Tujana nakiseldoh louva ahileh, jing jingkah leh nathi ding ahitai,” ati. \x + \xo 19:11 \xt Labu 59\x*
\v 12 Chuin ainneipi Michal in kotcha neo langa kon'in akhai lhan, ajamdoh in, ahoi dohtai.
\v 13 Hichun amanun milim khat alan, alupna ah ponsa khat asil peh’in, asam dingin kelcha mul asem peh in ahi.
\v 14 Chuin sottol le ho ahung uva David matding agot uleh, ainneipin adam hih in athou joupoi tin alep in ahi.
\v 15 Ahinlah Saul in asottol leho jah a thu apen, “Alupna a kon'in hinkaidoh un, kathading ahi,” atin ahi.
\v 16 Ahin alupna-a konna kaidoh ding agot uva aponsil chu agah hodoh uva ahileh, milim kisemthu, alua kelchamul chu amudoh tauve.
\v 17 Hijeh chun Saul in Michal jah a, “Ipibolla hitia hi nei joulhep’a, kagalmi keija konna najamdoh sah ham?” atin ahile, Michal in jong, “Aman neikithopi louva ahileh katha ding nahi eitijeh a kabol ahi,” tin ana donbut in ahi.
\v 18 David ajamdoh in Ramah khopi’ah achen Samuel to akimuto lhonin, chule Saul in achunga itobang tah’a na atoh ham ti aseipeh tan ahi. Samuel in David akilhonpin Ramah gamsunga Naioth mun’ah acheng tan ahi.
\v 19 David Ramah gamsunga Naioth mun'a aum'e ti thulhut Saul’in ana jatan ahi.
\v 20 Hichun aman David man dingin sottol-le ho asoltan ahi. Ahinlah amaho agalhun phat’un, Samuel lamkaina a themgao phabep in gaothu asei pet’u atohkha uvin, Saul sottol leho chu Pathen Lhagao chung uvah ahung chun, ama hon jong gaothu aseipan tauvin ahi.
\v 21 Chuin Saul in hichu ajahdoh kit phat’in, sottol dang ho asolkit in ahileh, ama hon jong gaothu aseiden kit tauvin ahi. Athumvei chan nan jong angai ngai ahiuve.
\v 22 Chuphat’in, Saul ama tah Ramah kho jonin achetai, Secu’a um twikul lentah phung ahin phah in, “Samuel le David hoiya um lhon em?” tin adongin ahile, “Ramah gam'a Naioth mun ah aum lhone,” tin mi koiham khat in ahin donbut in ahi.
\v 23 Ahin Ramah gam'a Naioth ajot chun, lampi’ah Pathen Lhagao Saul chungah ahung chun, Naioth alhun kahsen gaothu aseiyin ahi.
\v 24 Saul in apon abotkeh in, akeochang in tollhang ah alumin, Samuel angsung’ah sun nilhum jan khovah in gaothu asei in ahi. Chuin mihon aveuvin, adatmouvin, “Iti dana, Saul jeng jong themgao lah a jao hitam?” atiuvin ahi. \x + \xo 19:24 \xt 1 Samuel 10:11,12\x*
\c 20
\s1 Jonathan In David Akithopi
\p 
\v 1 David chu Ramah gam'a Naioth a kon'in ajamdoh’in, Jonathan kom ajonin, “Ipi kabol’a, Ipi kabol khel hitam? Itobang gitlouna ipi um’a napan tha dinga eihol le le ham?” ati.
\v 2 Jonathan in, “Hichu dihlou ahi, nangma thipon nate, abol ding jouse thilneo hihen lang thil len hijongleh kei hetlouvin ima abolji poi, eihetsah jinai. Kapan hitobang thil ho hi, kakom'a aselguh louhel ding ahi,” tin ana nelkal in ahi.
\v 3 Chuin David in Jonathan masang ah akihahsellin, “Napan iki golngai lhon hi kichentah’a ahetsohkei ahi, hijeh chun ama le ama akihouvin, Jonathan hetsah da tange, ipibolla alung kasuhnat ding ham? Ahinlah hingjing Pakai le nangma min pana kasei ahi keima le thina kikah hi kal khat seh bou uma ahi!” ati.
\v 4 Jonathan in, “Ipi ti kakithopi thei ding ham nei seipeh in,” ati.
\v 5 David in adonbut in, “Jing nikho hi lhathah kut ahin, lengpa to ankong umkhom dingdol kahi, ahin keima jing nikho tengleh loulaiya kakisela hichea chu nithum chan na nilhah tokah’a kaumden ding ahi,” ati. \x + \xo 20:5 \xt Minbu 28:11\x*
\v 6 “Napan hoiya che ham tia nahin doh’a ahileh, Bethlehem ain’ah kumseh kilhaina bol dingin kakom'ah phalna athum’in ache’e tin seipeh in,” ati.
\v 7 “Aman ‘Aphai!’ atia ahileh, thu anome ti nahet ding ahi. Ahinlah alung ahanna alung alhaso khah’a ahile, eithanom ahi ti nahet ding ahi.
\v 8 Lungset tah in hiti chun neibolpeh in, thengsel’a kahenga Pakai ang’a nakitepna nit’in. amavang napa douna a themmo kahile nangmatah in neithat jengin. Ahinlah nei joulhep hihbeh in,” ati.
\v 9 Jonathan in, “Hitobang chu agel in geldan, kapan chutobang’a nangma tha nading lunggel neocha hijongleh anei mong’a ahile, nang kahin mahetsah tei ding ahi,” ati.
\v 10 Chuin David in, “Napa alunghang’e ahilou le alunghang poi tichu ken iti kahet thei ding ham?” tin adongin ahi.
\v 11 Jonathan in adonbut’in, “Hungin loulai langa khun gapotdoh hite,” ati. Chule polam’ah akijotdoh khom lhonin ahi.
\v 12 Chuti chun Jonathan in David kom'ah, “Pakai Israel Pathen chu a hettohsah hijeng hen! Keiman jing tuphat don ahilouleh nithum joutengleh, kappa dongin katin, nachung alungdam nah le thu kahin thot ding,
\v 13 “Ahinlah ijem tia kappa alunghan’a nangma tha tei ding nagot’a, nangma na hindohtei tei nadinga keiman nahenga ka seipeh masat’a kasolmang lou poupouva ahileh Pakaiyin Jonathan kiti keima hi eibolsejo hen ahilou jongleh eithat jeng hen. Pakaiyin kapa ana umpi bangin nang jong naumpi hen,” ati.
\v 14 “Neingailut monga ahileh, kahinkho aumlai sungsen Pakai ngailutna sangtah in nei ngailun. Ahinlah kathia ahileh,
\v 15 Ka insung mite din tahsan umtah ngailutna sangtah in hin ngailun chule Pakaiyin nagalmite jouse jong leiset a kon'in suhmang gamkei hen,” ati. \x + \xo 20:15 \xt 2 Samuel 9:1\x*
\v 16 Hijeh chun Jonathan in David toh kitepna khat asemin, “Pakaiyin nagalmite jouse asugam keihen!” ati.
\v 17 Chule Jonathan in David chu ama aki ngailut bang banga angailut jeh chun, David in jong angailut din akitepsah kit tan ahi.
\v 18 Chuin Jonathan in, “Jing nikho le lhathah kut kimang ding ahin, natouna dokhang a-on jeh a nakiholmo ding ahi,” ati.
\v 19 “Athaini nilhah lam leh, tumasanga nakiselji na mun songpi pang mama’a chun che inlang gakisel tan.
\v 20 Chule keima kahungdoh’a doikhat neibanga, thalchang thum hiche panga chu kahinkap ding ahi,” ati.
\v 21 “Chule chapang khat thal chang ho hol ding’a kahinsol ding ahi. Chule chapangpa jah a, ‘Ven, thalchang ho chu nasihlam panga naum'e,’ tia kasei najah a ahile, hingjing Pakai min'a kasei ahi, abonchan aphasohkeiye, imacha hahsatna aumpoi.
\v 22 Amavang keiman ama jah a, “Gamla jepmah chen, thal chang chu nakhel lamah aum'e, katia ahile, nalampia gangtah in che jengin, ajeh chu Pakaiyin nasolmang ahi,” ti hetna ahi,” ati.
\v 23 “Chule Pakai a hettohsah ahijeh in, ikitepna vang chu Pakaiyin tonsot geiya einitsah teitei lhon hen,” ati
\v 24 Hiti chun David chu loulaiyah akisellin, chule lhathah kut kiman na ahunglhun phat in, Lengpa chu, anne dingin atou lhatan ahi.
\v 25 Chule lengpa chu nidanga bangin bangkom'a touna chunga chun atouvin ahi. Jonathan toh akimai ngatton, chule Abner asih-lang ah atouve. Ahin David touna chu a-ongtai.
\v 26 Ahinlah Saul in hicheni chun imacha aseipoi, ajeh chu ama chunga thil thenglou khattou David asuhboh hinte, tia alunggel ahi.
\v 27 Ahinlah, ajinga jong David touna a-on kit phat in, Saul in Jonathan jah a, “Ipi jeh a Jesse chapa janhia jong tunia jong hunglou hitam?” tin adongtai.
\v 28 Jonathan in, “David in Bethlehem a chedingin hatah in kakom'a phalna athumin,
\v 29 Aman, ‘Lungset tah in, neichesah in, ajeh chu ka insung miten kumseh a kho sunga gan kilhaina kaneidiu ahin, chule kasopi te hotoh jong kakimupi nom’e, tin ataovin ahi. Hijeh a chu lengpa dokhang’a atouna ong’ah ahi,” atin ahi.
\v 30 Chuin Jonathan chunga Saul alunghang behseh jengin, “Numei chaveinu chapa!” tin lunghang tah in ahousen ahi. “Nalunggel ho hi ken kahetlouva nagel ham? Nakhella lenga natungot ham? Nangma le nanu jumso pa,” ati.
\v 31 “Jesse chapa David ahinlai sungsen, nang leng’in pang thei pon nate. Tun chenlang gaholdoh in katha ding ahi,” ati.
\v 32 Jonathan in, “Ipi jeh a kithat ding ham? Aman ipi abolset ham?” tin apa adongin ahi.
\v 33 Chuin Saul in achapa Jonathan chu thadingin tengchan akho jengin ahi. Hichea kon chun Jonathan in jong apan David thading’a agot mong ahi tichu ahedoh tai.
\v 34 Hichun Jonathan chu lunghang tah in dokhang a kon'in akipatdoh in, apan ajachat sah behseh jeh chun chuche kut ni ni lhin nichun an ane tapoi, David chu alungkhampi lheh tan ahi.
\v 35 Ajing jingkah in David toh akitepna bangin, Jonathan chu chapang khat toh apotdoh lhonin, loujaova chun ache lhontai.
\v 36 Chuin aman chapangpa jah a chun “ka kapgot thalchang ho hi gaholdoh in,” ati. Chuin chapangpa chu alhaijel in ahile, Jonathan in akal langpeh a thalchang chu akap’in ahi.
\v 37 Chuin chapangpa chu Jonathan in akapdoh thalchang kom aphah phat ding kon'in, Jonathan in chapangpa jah-a, “Thalchang chu akal langpeh’ah achubouve,” atin ahi.
\v 38 Jonathanin chapangpa chu asamin, “Hikom'a chun dingden hih in, agang gangin hinchoi loiyin,” ati. Chuin chapangpa chun thalchangho chu achom khomin, apu henga ahungtai.
\v 39 Ahinlah chapangpa chun imacha ahepon, Jonathan le David in bou thil kibol ho chu ahet lhon ahi.
\v 40 Chuin Jonathan in amanchah ho chu chapangpa apen, chenlang khopi sungah anapolut in tin asoltai.
\v 41 Chuin chapangpa apotdoh doh in, songlhuh pang’a akiselna a kon'in David chu ahung potdoh'in, thumveijen tollah amai asulut in Jonathan maiyah akunin, anilhonin amitlhipum in akikolto lhonin ana kivailhah lhon tai.Hichu Jonathan sangin David apona dehset in ahi.
\v 42 Jonathan in David kom'ah, “Lungmong’in chetan, Pakai min'a thengsel’a ikihahsel lhon nang le kei, na chilhah te le keiya din, ikitepna chu tonsot geiyin Pakaiyin eikoi jing u hen,” ati. Hichun David in adalhan, chule Jonathan jong khopi lam’ah akile kittai.
\c 21
\s1 David Saul’a Kona Ajam
\p 
\v 1 David chu Ahimelech thempupa kimupi din Nob khopi’ah achen ahi. Ahimelech in David chu amu phat in ati anahot’in, “Itia nachangseh nahim? Ipi jeh a mikhatbeh in nahin kilhonpi louham?” tin ana dongin ahi. \x + \xo 21:1 \xt Matt 12:3,4; Mk 2:25,26; Lk 6:3\x*
\v 2 David in adonbut’in, “Lengpan kin chomkhat’a eihinsol ahi bouve, ipibol dia kahung hi koimacha hetsahlou dia eihil chah ahin, chule kasepaite chun katepna mun chom khat’a eikimupi diuva ka seipeh ahi,” ati
\v 3 “Nehle chah ipipi nanei em? Changlhah pheng nga ahilou le, nehthei adang ipi um'em neipen,” ati.
\v 4 Hichun thempu pan jong, adonbut in “Keihon changlhah mai mai kanei pouve, ahinlah koitobang nailamcha-a numeiya kisuboh louho dingin changlhah theng kanei uve,” ati.
\v 5 Hichun David in, “Lungkham hihin, keiman, kamite ho adeh’a galsat dinga akiche tengule, numeija konna kikangse louho kaphal jipoi, gamkhol mai mai kache tengu jong hiche thudol’a kisuboh ngailou ahiuve, achutile hiche khohsah tum neiya kholjinna’a iti thenda diu ham!” ati.
\v 6 Neh ding dang aumtah lou jeh'in, thempu pan changlhah kithensosa chu David apetai, ajeh chu changlhah Pathen a tosa bou chu anei ahin, hichu athah akito nitengleh changlhah chu kikhel dohji ahi. Chule hiche nikho nitah a chu thah ana kikoi khel ahi. \x + \xo 21:6 \xt Thempu Dan 24:5-9\x*
\v 7 Edomakon Doeg kiti mipa khat, Saul gancha ching lamkaipu khat anaum khan, Hou-In mun’abol lhing ding kin aneijeh in anaumden khan ahi.
\v 8 David in Ahimeleh jah a, “Nakom'a tengcha ahilou le chemjam um'em? Lengpa kin’a kigoman louva kahung ahin, manchah ima kahin choilou ahi!” ati.
\v 9 Hichun Ahimelech in, “Elah phaicham’a nathana pa, Philistine mipa Goliath chemjam bou chu kanei’e; hikom'a thempu von kikoina nunglam’a khun pon’in akichun in aum'e, nadeilekilah in, adangvang aumpoi” ati. Chuin David in ajah a, “Hichu neipen! Chusang’a phajo le hoijo chemjam adang umponte,” ati. \x + \xo 21:9 \xt 1 Samuel 17:51\x*
\v 10 Hichun David Saul kom'a kon'in ajamdoh’in, Gath khopi Achish lengpa heng ajontan ahi.
\v 11 Ahinlah Achish lenggam sung’a lamkaiho chu akom uva aum ding chu akipah pouvin ahi. \x + \xo 21:11 \xt 1 Samuel 18:7; 29:5\x*
\p ama hon, “Hiche mipa hi agamsung’a leng changsa David chu hilou haimo? Miho lamuva, ama chung changa hi la asah uva Saul in mi asang asangin athat’in, David in vang sangsom somin athat’e, tia alachoipao chu hilou ham?” tin adonguve.
\p 
\v 12 Hiche athuseiho chu David in ajah phat’in Gath lengpa Achish chu akicha lheh jeng tan ahi. \x + \xo 21:12 \xt Labu 56\x*
\v 13 Hijeh chun David jong aki ngolsah’in, kotpi phungdung ho chu ajihpolin, chule akhalhang dunga achilphon akaisah deh duhin jengin ahi. \x + \xo 21:13 \xt Labu 34\x*
\v 14 Achaina in Achish lengpan amite ho kom'ah, “Hitobang mingol chu kahenga nahung sah’u ham?
\v 15 Kakimvella hitobang mingol kanei louva nabollu ham? Ipi dinga motchon chon a eisuboi ding bep’a ka-insunglai tah’a, kamasang’a hiche pa hinpuilut nahiuvam?” tin ahung eojah jengin ahi.
\c 22
\s1 Adullam Songko Sung’a David
\p 
\v 1 Hiti chun David in Gath adalhan Adullama songko sungah akisel’in ahi. Asopite le apa insung mite jousen ajahphat un ahengah achesuh un ahi. \x + \xo 22:1 \xt Labu 57; 142\x*
\v 2 Chuin bol hesoh thoh, aleiba, alung genthei jouse le lunglhai louna jousen David chu ahin bel un ahile amaho chu jali tobang ahung lhing’un, David chu amaho lamkaiyin apangtan ahi.
\v 3 Chujouvin David Moab gam'a Mizpeh kho’ah achen, hia chun aman lengpa jah a, “Pathen'in kachunga ipi abol ding kahet toh masangin, nakom'ah kanu le kapa nangho kom'a achen theina din neiphal peh in,” tin ngehna aneiyin ahi.
\v 4 Hiti chun David songko sunga aum sungsen, anule apa chu Moab lengpa kom'ah aum lhone.
\v 5 Nikhat Gad themgao pan David kom'a, “Songko sungah umden hih’in naum’na dalhan lang Judah gam lang’ah chetan,” ati. Hichun David akipatdoh paiyin Hareth gamsung ajon tan ahi.
\v 6 Judah gamsung ahunglut taiti thusoh Saul in ana jatan ahi. Hiche pettah’a chu Saul lengpa chu Gibeah khoa huisum phung noi khat’a ana toupet ahin, akhutah tengcha akichoiya, gal lamkailen ho akimvel’a tou uva ahi.
\v 7 Hiche thusoh ajah phat chun, Saul chun alamkai lenho masang ah hatah in asamin, “Ngaitem’un Benjamin mite ho! David in na boncha uva loule lengpilei pedia kitem em? Asepaite lamkaiya pansah nadia kitem em?” ati.
\v 8 “Hiche ho jeh a hi nang hon keima tha nadia lungthim nanei u ham? Kachapan Jesse chapatoh kitepna aneilhon chun, koima chan seipeh ding neigo pouve, keima dingin jong neigelkhoh peh pouve. Phaten kingai touvin! Kachapa tah injong eitha nadingin atilkhou vin, eichanglhi lelen, ahinlah koima chan jong nei seipeh pouve,” ati.
\v 9 Chutahchun Doeg kiti Edom mipa chu Saul toh anading khom lhonin, “Keiman Nob’a kana umlaiyin Jesse chapa chu ahungin, Ahitub chapa Ahimelech thempupa toh akihoulim lhon jong kamui,” ati. \x + \xo 22:9 \xt 1 Samuel 21:7-9; Labu 52\x*
\v 10 Chule Ahimelech chun David din Pakai adohpeh’in chujongleh neh ding jong aluipeh in, Philistine mihatpa Goliath chemjam jong apei,” ati.
\s1 Thempu Teho Kitha
\p 
\v 11 Chuin Saul lengpan jong Ahitub chapa Ahimelech le ainkote chule Nob gamsung’a thempu kin bol jouse man dingin mi asoltan ahi.
\v 12 Aman a cheho ahung lhun phat’un, Saul’in lunghang tah in, “Ahitub chapa ngaijin! Hichun Ahimelech in jong, “Lengpa ipi thu hitam?” tin adongin ahi.
\v 13 Saul in, “Ipi jeh a nang le Jesse chapan keidou na’a na natoh lhon ham? Ipi jeh a neh ding le chemjam napeh ham? Ipi jeh a ama dinga Pathen kom'a nadohpeh ham? Ipi jeh a kei tha nadinga natilkhou ham? Tua eidouva, kei that dia changpang jing ahi,” ati.
\v 14 Ahimelech in adonbut in, “Ahinlah kapu, nasohte holah a hi koi pentah hi natupa David banga kitah um am? David chu navengtup holah a lamkai hiya chule leng inpi sung’a mitin in ajapentah hilou ham?” ati.
\v 15 “Ken ama dinga Pathen henga thudoh kabolpeh hi tuchunga hi apatna jong ahi tapoi. Ahinlah hiche chung change hin lengpan kei le ka insung mite neingoh thei pouvin te ajeh chu nang douna le tha nadia thil kigong ho hi khat’a khatcha kahepha poi.” Ati.
\v 16 Hiche tah chun lengpan jong Ahimelech jah ah, “Nathi teitei ding ahi, nangjong na insung mite jouse jong na boncha uva nathi teitei diu ahi,” tin ahohsal tai.
\v 17 Chule lengpan akom'a ding ama ngah’a pang sepai pa jah a chun, “Pakai thempuho hi that gam jengin, ijeh-inem itile, amaho jong hi David toh kikhutjop cheh ahiuve ajeh chu David ajamtai ti ahesohkeijun, ahinlah eiseipeh pouve!” ati. Ahinlah Saul sepaite ho chun Pakai thempuho tha jeng ding chu akhut alhaang ngam tapouvin ahi.
\v 18 Hichun lengpan Doeg jah a, “Nangin bol jengin,” atile, Edom mipa Doeg chun hiche nikho chun thempu vona kivon Pakai thempu som get le nga anathat gam’in ahi.
\v 19 Chuin thempuho chenna Nob’ah achen, thempu ho insung mit jouse abouchauvin numeile pasal, chapangle nao noicheplai, bongchal jouse le sangante, kekngoiho geijin athatgam hel tan ahi.
\v 20 Ahin Ahimelech chapa te lah a amin Abiathar kitipa bouseh chu ajamdoh man’in David kom'ah anajamlut tai.
\v 21 Saul in Pakai thempu jouse athagam chu Abiathar in David kom'ah aseipeh tai.
\v 22 Hichun David in jong Abiathar jah ah, “Edom mipa Doeg kamu nia patna chu Saul jah-a aseitei tei ding kahetsa ahitai, keiman napa insung mite aboncha kathilosah ahitai.
\v 23 Keima kom'a um'in, kicha hih’in, keiman kahinkho phal ngam in navengbit nange, ajeh chu nangma thadinga naholpan, keijong tha dinga eihol ahi,” tin aseipeh tan ahi.
\c 23
\s1 David In Keilah Khopi Ahuhdoh
\p 
\v 1 Nikhat David heng’ah thu ahunglhungin, Philistine miten Keilah kho abulu-uvin, chule changpholla chang jouse jong akichomgam tauve, ahung tiuve.
\v 2 David in Pakai kom'a, “Kagache a kagasat ding ham?” tia adohle, Pakaiyin ahindonbut in, “Henge, chenlang Keilah khopi khu ga huhdoh in,” ati.
\v 3 Ahinlah David asepaiten ajah a, “Ven eiho Judah gamsung jenga jong kichatah’a um ihiuvin, i-atileh Keilah khoa icheuva hiche Philistine sepaite khujatpi khutoh ikisatto pi thei diu ham?” atiuve.
\v 4 Hijeh chun David in jong Pakai adongkit in ahile, Pakaiyin ajah a, “Keilah ah kumsuh un, ajeh chu keiman kapanpia Philistine mite najo dingu ahi,” ati.
\v 5 Hijeh chun David le asepaite jong Keilah khopi’ah acheuvin, Philistine te agasat’un, mi tamtah agathat tauve, chule agancha jouseu ahin kikai’un chule Keilah kho miho jong ahuhdoh un ahi.
\v 6 Ahimelech chapa Abiathar chu Keilah khopia konna ahung jamdoh’a David kom ahin jot chun, Thempuvon ompho khat ahin kipohlut in ahi.
\v 7 David chu Keilah khoah ahung luttai tithu Saul’in ajah phat in, “Aphalheh jenge! Tuavang hi Pathen'in kakhutna apehdoh ahitai, ajeh kulpi kaikhumsa, kulpi kikamkhum sung’a David hi ama amachama hung vahlut ahitai,” ati.
\v 8 Hitah chun Saul in asepaite jouse akhom khom sohkeiyin, Keilah khopi chu ahin nokhum’un, David le asepaite chu aumkhum tauvin ahi
\v 9 Ahinlah David in Saul thilgon jouse chu ahen, Abiathar thempupa jah ah, “Thempuvon ompho chu hikom'ah hinchoiyin,” ati.
\v 10 Chuin David in, “Vo Pakai Israel Pathen, keima hiche mun'a kaum jeh hin Saul in Keilah khopia hung’a akhopi hi suhchim ding tohgon aneiyin ahi.
\v 11 Hiche kho mite hin keima hi amaho khutna eipehdoh diu ham? Chule Saul hung mong ding hinam? Vo Pakai Israel Pathen, lungsettah in nei seipeh in,” tin ataovin ahi. Chuin Pakaiyin,“Hung ding ahi,” tin adonbut in ahi.
\v 12 David’in jong, “Keilah khopia lamkaiho hin, keima le kasepaite ho hi Saul khutna eipeh doh dingu ham?” tin adong kit’in ahi. Chule Pakaiyin, “Henge ama hon napehdoh dingu ahi,” tin ahin donbut in ahi.
\s1 David Thinglhang’a Akisel
\p 
\v 13 David le amite ho chu jagup vel alhinphat'un, Keilah mun chu adalhauvin thinglhang lang’ah apotdoh’u le David chu jamdoh tai tithu chu Saul lengpan ajahdoh phat in Keilah khopi lam chu anajon tapoi.
\v 14 David vang chu gamthip lah ah munthip khat’ah aumin, Ziph gamthip thinglhang gamlah ah chun apansa dentai.
\v 15 Nikhat chu Horesh kom vella David aum pet in, Saul chun David tha ding hollin Ziph lam ahin jon touve tithu ajantan ahi.
\v 16 Hichun Jonathan in jong David kimupia Pathen tahsan tah’a dingdet kheh dingin atilkhou dingin ahol in ahi.
\v 17 tin Jonathan’in, “Kicha hih in, kapan namudoh jouponte! Nangma Israel te leng nahung hi ding ahi, keima kapa banga nang bana kahi ding ahi, hichu kappa Saul in ahet ahi,” tin ana tilkhouvin ahi.
\v 18 Hijeh chun amanin Pakai masang ah kitepna khat anei lhonin ahi. Chuin Jonathan ain lamah akilen, David vang chu Horesh mun ah aumdentai. \x + \xo 23:18 \xt 1 Samuel 18:3\x*
\v 19 Chujouvin Ziph miho chu Gibeah mun'a Saul hengah acheuvin, David chu apedoh tauvin ahi. “Keihon kiselna mun kaheuve, Ama tuhin Jeshimon lhanglam’a um Hakilah thinglhang gam sung, Horesh kulpi dunga keiho lah a David kisel ahi,” atiuvin ahi. \x + \xo 23:19 \xt Labu 54\x*
\v 20 “Vo lengpa naki got chaiya nakigin phat phat’a nahung konsuh’a ahile keihon jong jaonan napanpi ving ting, David chu nangma khut’a pedoh nauvinge,” aga tiuvin ahi.
\v 21 Hichun Saul in jong, “Pakaiyin phatthei naboh’u hen, ajeh chu nang hon hibangtah’a keima ding neihin gel khohpeh uve.
\v 22 Cheloiyunlang, phate chan gaphochen un, aumna mun, age namun, gahechen set uvin unlang gavechil chet tauvin, ajeh chu, ama hi mi kilep themtah ahi.
\v 23 Hijeh chun akisel namun hoilai ham ti, gavechilsohkeijuvin ima jouse he sohkei uvin lang, kahenga hungkit uvin, chutengleh keijong, nangho toh kilhona icheuva agamsunga David aumpou pouva ahileh kahol doh teitei ding ahi,” ati.
\v 24 Hijeh chun amaho jong akipatdoh uvin Ziph gamlanga chun Saul sang'in anache masa tauve. David le asepaite chu hiche pet’a hi Jeshimon lhang lama Arabah gamsung Ma’on gammang noiya kisel’ah ahiuve.
\v 25 Saul le amiten aholle leuve ti David in ajahdoh phat in, gamthip sunglam agamla jep songpi lentah khat sungah alutin, Maon gamthip ah aum tan ahi. Ahinlah Saul chun ana hol jingin ahi.
\v 26 Chuin Saul le amite molpang langkhat ah achen, hibangma chun David le aloiho jong molpang lang khat ah acheuvin, chuin Saul le aloiho chun, David le amite chu nailutna matdin aumkul tauvin ahi.
\v 27 Ahin Saul heng ah thusoh kin khat ahunglhungin, ajah ah, “Gangtah in hungin jeh chu Philistine ten gamsung gal hin boltauve,” tin ahung seijun ahi.
\v 28 Hijeh chun David nung adella kon'in Saul akinunglen, Philistine te satdin achetai. Hijeh chun hiche mun chu Sela-hammahlekoth asah tauvin ahi.
\v 29 Chuin David chua kon chun achetouvin Engedi mun dettah sunga achengtai.
\c 24
\s1 David In Saul Hinkho Ahinghoi
\p 
\v 1 Saul in Philistine mite agasat-a ahung kile jouvin, David En-gedi gamthip mun’ah aluttai tithu aseipeh tauvin ahi.
\v 2 Hijeh chun Saul in Israel mite jousea kon'in galsat them cheh mi sangthum akilhen doh’in David le amite holdingin gam-kelcha umna songkol lang’ah aga hol tauvin ahi.
\v 3 Saul chu ahunga ahile lampia kelngoi honlah khat agatoh khan, hiche laiya chun songkohom khat aumin, hikom'a chu chomkhat kicholdo din aluttai, hiche songko sunga adan sungnung lang ma ma-a chu David le aloite kisella uma ahi. \x + \xo 24:3 \xt Labu 57; 142\x*
\v 4 David aloihon ajah a guhthimin, “Tuhi nang dia phat kijen petcha ahi! Tunia hi Pakaiyin asei, ‘Keiman namel mapa chu nakhut’a kapeh duha, nangman naphatsah lamlama nabol ding ahi.’tia asei nikho chu tunia hi hunglhunga ahitai,” atiuve. Hijeh chun David jong akipatdoh in, kangchan akithol thol’in, Saul sangkhol chol mong chu aga-at tan peh tan ahi.
\v 5 Ahin David in Saul sangkhol chol mong chu aga-at tan chu alungsunga nommo asan ahi.
\v 6 Hijeh chun amite jah a, “Pakaiyin ahet ahi, hiche hi kanabol louding dol ahi, ajeh chu ama hi ka pakai le kaleng ahi. Pakaiyin adeilou, ka Pakai le ka lengpa chunga hiche kabol hi alhendohsa le athaonu doudal kahi,” atin ahi. \x + \xo 24:6 \xt 1 Samuel 26:11\x*
\v 7 Hijeh chun David in a sepaite chu atuhtang nah nah in, Saul chu atha sah tapon ahi. Saul athouvin songko adalha a, alampi’ah akiche phat- in,
\v 8 David ahung potdoh'in anungjuiyin asamin, “Ka pakai le lengpa!” atileh Saul ahung kihei phat’in ama jabolnan David tol’a abohkhup in chibai aboh in ahi.
\v 9 Chule, hitin Saul jah a asamin, “Ipibolla nangin mipi ho thusei na ngaiya, keihin nang chu kasuhgenthei dana nagel ham?
\v 10 Tuni nikhotah jeng’a jong nangman namit tah in namun ahi, hichu atahbeh ahi. Ajeh chu Pakaiyin kei khotona noiyah songko sung jenga jong nakoijin ahi. Kamite ho phabep khat in katha ding hitam tia eidohuva, kana noplou ahi. Ipi jeh inem itileh, ‘keiman ka lengpa sugenthei louding kahi-ama hi Pakai thaonu sa ahi,’
\v 11 Ven kapa, kakhutna ipi kachoi em? na sangkholchol among kachelhah chu bou kachoi ahi bouve, nathat pong kate. Nasugenthei pong kate ti vetsahna’a keiman nangma kasuhgenthei louding chule nangin thadingin nei dal le le jong lechun na chunga kachonset louding ahi,” ati.
\v 12 “Pathen chu eini kaha ahetoh, athutan ahi. Ijemtia kei chunga nabolla ahile Pathen'in gotna napeh ding ahi, ahinlah ken vang nang kasuhgenthei louding ahi.
\v 13 Thuchih luiyin khat in, ‘Miphalou hoa kon'in, thil phalou tohdoh in aum'e,’ ati. Hijeh chun nang dounan itihchan hijongleh kakhut kalap louding ahi.
\v 14 Israel lengpa chu koipen nunga hung hija, koipen thunung nahin dal mong mong ham? Uicha thisa khat tou ham, uili khattou nung dal nahim? \x + \xo 24:14 \xt 1 Samuel 26:20\x*
\v 15 Hijeh chu Pakai chu thutan in pang henlang, kei le nang kikah’ah thutan pa hijing jeng hen,” ati.
\v 16 Chuin David in aseiding jouse asei jou phatin, Saul in ahin donbut in, “Thu hin sei a chu chapa David mong mong nahi hinam?” atin akap pantan ahi.
\v 17 Chule David kom'a aseiyin, “Nang hi kei sangin nadih e, ajeh chu keiman na chunga thil phalou jeng kabollin ahin nangman vang thilpha jengin nei lethuh jing jenge,” atitai.
\v 18 “Henge, nangman hepina dihtah in tunin nei ngailun, nei tha theina ding laitah a jong neithat pon ahi.
\v 19 Hitobang hi mihem khat’in amelma pa ato khah’a ahile, damsella alhadoh mong mong ding hinam? Hijeh chun tunia kei dinga thilpha naboldoh jeh in, Pakaiyin thilpha nabolpeh teitei hen.
\v 20 Chule tun keiman kichentah in kahetai, nangma Israel te leng nahung hitei tei ding ahi.
\v 21 Hijeh chun tunin Pakai minin kahenga kitep’in, ‘Kathi nungle ka insung jong na hinghoiya, kakhanggui le kachilhah jong nei hoi peh teijin!” ati.
\v 22 Chuin David jong Saul kom'a akihahsel in, hichun Saul jong inlam ajon tan; David le asepai chengse akulpiu mun'a akaltou tauvin ahi.
\c 25
\s1 Samuel Thi
\p 
\v 1 Tun Samuel athitan ahile Israel mite jouse avui dingin ahung kikhom un, athilong chu a-op uvin, Ramah khoa a-inah avui tauvin ahi.
\s1 Nabal In David Asuh Lunghan
\p Hichun David chu Maon gamthip ah akumsuh tan ahi.
\p 
\v 2 Maon a kon nei le gou tampi neiyah mihaothei tah khat Carmel khopia kiveina bol mi khat aum'inahi. Ama chun kelngoi sang thum chule kelcha sangkhat aneiyin ahi chule hiche phatlai chu kelmulvo phatlai ahi.
\v 3 Hiche mipa min chu Nabal akitin, ajinu min chu Abigail akitin ahi, Ajinu chu numei chingtah ahin, thil umdan hekhen themtah jong ahin, amel jong mel-hoi tah ahi. Ajipa vang chu Caleb phungmi, umdan, chondan helou mi ahin, agiloutah a chon jeng ahi.
\v 4 Nabal kitipa hin kelngoi avah’e ti hi David in ahedoh tan ahi.
\v 5 Hijeh chun David in gollhang somkhat asolin Nabal henga thuthot le salam gabol din asol in ahi.
\v 6 Hichun gollhangho chun, “Chamna le khantouna nang le na insunga chule naneile nanga chengse chunga umhen!” atiuvin ahi.
\v 7 “Nangman kelngoi mulvou ding miho chu keiho Carmel kom'a nakoiye ti kajan, keihon suh gentheina ima kanei pouve chule amahoa kon'in jong ima guhle lah kanei pouve.
\v 8 Namite ho dong jong le chun adihtah chu naseipeh nauvinte. Golvah nikho khat le kahung diu ahin, kipah tah a neisan diu David in adeiye. Lungset tah in napeh thei thei neipeuvin, nalhacha keiho le nagol ngaitah keima David min'in,” ati.
\v 9 David gollhangho chun David minin hicheng chu Nabal henga alhut uvin chule ama hon Nabal donbutna angahuvin ahi.
\v 10 Nabal in jong noise tah in, “David kitipa chu koi hija ham? Hiche Jesse chapa hin ama le ama ipia kigel ham? Tulaiya hi soh tamtah apakai teu henga konna jam mang atam e.
\v 11 Achutile, iti keiman kakelngoi mulvou’a pangho kathapeh kelngoi-sa, a twidon ding u chule aneh diu kachanglhah jouse hi kalahpeh’a, kahetphah lou gam'a hungkon miho chu kapeh beh ding hija ham?” ati pen tai.
\v 12 Hichun David gollhangho chu ahung kinunglen, Nabal in asei jouse chu David heng’ah alhut tauvin ahi.
\v 13 Chuin David in, “Na chemjam kigotun,” atin, hichun mi jali toh akilhon’un, chule mi jali anunglam uva thilkeo ngah din adalha uvin ahi.
\v 14 Hichun Nabal soh ho lah-a mi khat in Abigail aga hetsah in, “David in gamthip gam'a kon'in gollhangho kapu kom'a salam boldin asollin ahileh anaphoh sal in,
\v 15 Gollhang ho chu keiho dinga phattah ahiuve, keihon amahoa kon'in hahsatna imacha katoh khapouve, kaum khom sung uvin jong keihoa kon'in imacha alahdoh-u jong aumpoi.
\v 16 Sunle jan in keiho leh kelngoiho dingin baang bangineihong jingun, eingah tup jing uve.
\v 17 Hiche thu ho hi nangman nahet chet angaiye chule ipi bolding ham ti nagel angaiye, ajeh chu ka pakai pa le a insung mite jousea ding’a thil hahsa hungsoh dingin akilome. Amala alungtong lheh inkoimacha to kihou tehi ahipoi,” ati.
\v 18 Hichun Abigail gangtah in changlhah lhon jani akigot in, lengpitwi savun peng ni dimset agongin, honminsa kelngoi nga akigot in, changpoh kana atena dim nga agon, lengpithei changlhah boh jakhat toh, theichang changlhah a kisem jani, hciheng hi, amanun sangan chungah asemin,
\v 19 Asohte jah ah, “Anache masauvin, keiman kahin juipai ding nahiuve,” ati.
\v 20 Abigail chu asangan chunga atouvin molchunga akaltouvin, aman David le amite ama langa-a ahung chu amun ahi.
\v 21 David in, “Hiche Nabal kitipa gancha jouse chu keiman khatcha beh jong manthah sah louva gammang noija kachinpeh chu pan nabeija kabol dan ahitai, tun Nabal in kathilpha bol jouse thilsen eihin lethoh pehtai.
\v 22 Jingkah teng Nabal mi ahi kiti tapou pasal khatna khat jeng cha jong hinghoi louva katha gam louva ahile, Pakaiyin keima David hi eithat jeng hen,” tin aseitai.
\s1 Abigail Nabal Dia David Henga Atao
\p 
\v 23 Abigail in David amu phat’in, asangan chunga kon'in akumlhan amasang ah akunin abohkhup’in jana apen ahi.
\v 24 Akengphang bul’a abohkhup in ajah-a, “ka pakai thilsoh hicheng ho hi keima themmona ahijenge, chule nahenga kasei hi, neingaipeh-in.
\v 25 Hiche Nabal hi milungtong le mipha ahipoi, thupitah in lahih-in, ajeh chu ama hi mingol ahi bouve amin tobang banga ama jong hija ahi. Ahinla kapun nahinsol gollhangho chu nasoh nun kana mulou ahi,” ati.
\v 26 “Tujenginjong Pakai hingjing min'a kasei ahi, kapu jong nahin laihin Pakaiyin thisan so’a themmo sahna ding jousea nahoidoh sah ahitan, nakhut tah’a phu nalah ding jong aphal lousa ahitai, hijeh chun suhset ding thadinga nahola namelmate jouse chu Nabal tobang hisohkei uhen.
\v 27 Nasoh nu keiman hiche nangma le nagollhang ho neh le chah dia kahin poh hi kapu neisanpeh tei teiyin.
\v 28 Nasohnu hi ipi hile kathemmona aum leh abonchan nei ngaidam in. Pakai dia galsat nahijeh in Pakaiyin nang le na chilhah te lenga natun jing uhen chule nahinkho lhumkeiyin thilse bolda jengin,” ati.
\v 29 “Midang hon thadingin hung kipat u henlang, nahol hol jeng jong leu, kapu nahinkho hi Pakai na Pathen'in nei le gou manlutah bangin naven tup jingin ahi. Ahin namelma te ho jouse gophel a songchang kikap mang bang’a akap mang ding ahi.
\v 30 Chujongleh nachung chang thudol'a Pakaiyin aseisa jouse chu kapu dinga nabolpeh sohkeiya, Israel chunga lenga natun tengleh,
\v 31 Hitobang ho hi hi nolnabei nahina chu kipuisetsah hihin. Chutile ajeh beiya mitha jeh ham ahilou le nangin naphu nakilah jeh ham a nalung gimpi louding ahi. Chuleh Pakaiyin kapu nangma chung’a phatecha-a nainchen sah tengleh, nasohnu keijong neihin geldoh tei teiyin,” ati.
\v 32 David in Abgail adonbutin, “Tunia Israel Pathen'in keito kimuto dinga nahinsol jeh in, Pakai chu thangvah in umhen!
\v 33 Thil nahet them jeh in Pathen thangvah in umhen! Nangma jong phatthei chang in, ajeh chun nangman tuni hin kathemmona ding thisan kaso’a kei le kei phulah na’a kakhut kalap nadinga kon'in nei huhdoh tai.
\v 34 Pakai Israel Pathen min a kasei ahi, Pakaiyin nangho eisuhsetda sah ahitai, neihung kimupi loi hih le chu, jingkhovah masang’a Nabal mite khat a khatcha kahinghoi loud ing kathagam heldiu ahitai,” ati.
\v 35 Hichun David in jong athilpeh chengse akisan in, chule amanu jah-ah, “Lungmong tah-in na-inlama chetan, keiman nathusei kangai peh in, na inneipu jong katha louding ahitai,” ati.
\v 36 Hiti chun Abigail ahungkile kitna ain agalhun phat in, Nabal chun a insungah lengpa golvah ni bangin kut anabollin ahi. Ama chu ju hakham in akhamin, hijeh chun amanun jong ajing jingkah chan geiyin David toh akimuto thu jong aseipeh tapoi.
\v 37 Jingkah khovah lhah’a Nabal jong ajukhamna a konna hung limdoh phat in, ajinun thilsoh umchan jouse chu abonchan aseipeh tan ahileh atija behseh jengin, alungsunga alung achat tapon, songtum bangin akitung dentai.
\v 38 Nisom jouvin, Pakaiyin Nabal chu adeng in, athipai pai tai.
\s1 Daivd In Abigail Akichenpi
\p 
\v 39 David in Nabal thi ajah phat in, “Pakai thangvah in umhen, Nabal khutna konna jumsona hiche Nabal chunga phu eilahpeh chu nunnom hen. Nabal in achonset man akisan ahitai,” ati. Chuin David in Abigail henga aji hina dingin thuthot aneiyin, agadoh sah tan ahi.
\v 40 Chuin thupole ho chu Carmel alhun phat un, Abigail jah a, “David in jia neidia, nang puiya eihinsol’u ahi,” agatiuve.
\v 41 Hichun Abigail chu tol’ah abohkhup’in hitin adonbut in, “Kei, nasohnu, David toh kakichen ding kakipah’e, alhacha hiya akeng soppeh dia gotsa kahi,” ati.
\v 42 Abigail jong lungkin tah-in akigongin, akipatdoh pai paiyin, sangan chung khat’a akaldoh in ama jenlea pangji asoh numei nga chu akipuiyin, David sohte nung ajuijin, David ji- dingin apangtai.
\v 43 David chun Ahinoam Jezreel kho mi jong akichenpin, anigel lhonin, ajidin apang lhontai.
\v 44 Hiche kahlah chun Saul chun achanu Michal kitinu, David jinu chu Gallim kho mi Palti chapa La’ish chu aji din ape tai. \x + \xo 25:44 \xt 2 Samuel 3:14-16\x*
\c 26
\s1 David In Saul Avella Ahinghoi Kit
\p 
\v 1 Mi phabep Ziph a kon'in Saul kimupi dingin Gibeah mun ah ahung’un, “David chu Jeshimon nisolama Hakilah mol chunga chu kisel ahi,” ahung tiuve. \x + \xo 26:1 \xt Labu 54\x*
\v 2 Hijeh chun Saul in galsat themcheh Israel sepai sangthum akipuiyin David hol dingin Jiph gammang lam ajonsuh tauvin ahi.
\v 3 Saul chun Jeshimon nisolama Hakilah molchung lamlen pang a David kisel namun’a chun ngahmun akisemin ahi. Ahin David chun Saul in gammang noiyah ahung holle ti ahedoh tan ahi.
\v 4 Saul chu ahung mong nai ti photoh dingin guhthim in mi asollin ahi.
\v 5 Jankhat David chu Saul umna ngahmun chu kholchil ache in, aven ahileh, Saul, Ner chapa Abner chule a sepai jalamkai chu asung ah alumin, sepaiho chun akollin, akimvellah akigolun un ahi.
\v 6 Chuin David in Hit mipa Ahimelech chule Zeruiah chapa Joab sopipa Abishai jah a, “Saul ngahmun lailunga khu koipentah in kipedoh’a ei kilhon pi ding ham?” tia adoh a ahile Abishai in. “ Keiman nakilhon oi nange,” tin ahin donbut in ahi.
\v 7 Hijeh chun David le Abishai chu Saul umna ngahmun sung’ah alut lhonin ana imut pettah’u agatoh lhonin, ngahmun lailung achun Saul alumin, alukhap kom'a chun atengcha tolla ana kiphut’in, chule Abner le asepaite chu Saul kimvellah ana imu uvin ahi.
\v 8 Hichun Abishai in David kom'a o nemtah in, “Tunia hi Pathen'in namelma pa nangma khutna napeh doh ahitai, Keiman ama hi nivei sut ngai louvin, khatvei seh seh sun ingting leitoh sutbeh tange!” ati.
\v 9 Ahin David in, “Bollou ding ahi, Natha louding ahi. Pakai thaonusa douna-a akhut lama tapou chu koimacha athemmo louding aumpoi,” tin ana phoh in ahi.
\v 10 “ Hingjing Pathen min'a kasei ahi, nikhat tengleh Pathen'in Saul hinjep nem tei nante ahilou le tehthi nante ahilou le gal’a thi ding ahi.
\v 11 Pathen thaonu khat katha ding chu Pakaiyin ajah nompoi! Ahinlah atengcha le alukhap kom'a atwipai vang kilah in, chuteng hia kon'in dalha hitin cheta hite!” ati. \x + \xo 26:11 \xt 1 Samuel 24:6\x*
\v 12 Hijeh chun David in tengcha le Saul alu kom'a twipai chu alan chule ama le Abishai chu koimacha hetlou kah’in achemang lhon tai, ajeh chu Pakaiyin Saul mite alhim imut ngoideh sah ahi.
\v 13 David a ngahmun gallang’u mol’ah akal touvin akiven phah nachan agei lhonin,
\v 14 Sepai ho leh Ner chapa Abner jah din, “Abner, kithouvin!” tin ahin samin ahile “Koi nahim?” tin Abner in adonbut in adongin ahi.
\v 15 David in, “Aphai Abner, nangma milen, nahilou ong? Nanghi pasal nahi hilou ham? Israel lah a hi nang tobang mimo koi umkha am? Ipi dinga nangman napu lengpa chu phatecha nahon tup lou ham? Ajeh chu mipi lah a khat hi napu lengpa thatdin hungleh,
\v 16 Hiche hi phaloubeh ahi! Pakai hingjing min'a kasei ahi, nang le, lengpa athisa tobang nahi lhontai, ajeh chu nangman na pakai-pa naventup jou tah lou jeh in na losamtai. Napakai, na leng, Pakai thaonu a tengcha le alulhuna atwipai jong phaten koitup peh tangem?” tin ahin samin ahi.
\v 17 Saul in David ogin ahi chu ahen, “Kachapa David chu nahilou haimo?” ahin tin ahile David in adonbutin, “Henge ka pakai le lengpa, Ibola ba nei chanle le ham? Ipi kabolset em? Kathepmona ipi ham?
\v 19 Ahin tun ka pakai le ka lengpa nasohpa thusei hi ngaiyin, Pakaiyin kei douna’a natildoh ahi vang leh ka maicham eisan peh hen. Achuti louva mihem tildoh mai mai ahivang leh, ajao tapou Pakaiya kon'in gaosap changhen. Ajeh chu ama hon kain mun'a kon'in ei kidal mang un, Hijeh chun Pakai mitetoh kaum khom thei tapoi, chule gamchom mite pathen houtan eitiuve.
\v 20 Pathen’a konna gamla tah a gamdang mite ho gamsunga kathi ding hitam? Ipi jeh a chu Israel lengpa chu uili khat holle a hugn kipatdoh ham? Ipi jeh a kei hi molsang vum'a lhanlha adal bangineidal jeng ham?” atin ahi.
\v 21 Chuin Saul in, “Keiman kabol khel tai, inlam’ah hung kile tan, kachapa, keiman tukal nasugim taponge, tunin kahinkho hi nei hinghoi peh kit tai. Keima angol tobang chule suh khelna tamtah kana neitai,” tin Saul in ahin donbut’e.
\v 22 David in, “Vo lengpa, Hichea hin na tengcha aum'e, Khangdong mikhat hinsol inlang hung la hen.
\v 23 Pakaiyin midih le kitah neiho adungjuijin kipaman apehjin ahi. Tunin jong Pakaiyin nangma chu kei khutna eipehsa ahitan, hijongleh keiman Pakai thaonusa lengpa chunga kakhut kalap louhel ding ahi.
\v 24 Ven tunia keima mitmua nangma hinkho manlutah kahisah bang chun keima hinkho jong Pakai mitmun manlutah hijeng henlang, Pakaiyin thoh hahsa kathohna changsea kon'in eihuhdoh tei teihen,” ati.
\v 25 Chuphat in Saul jong chun David jah a, “Kachapa David nunnom in! Nanghin thil tamtah nahin bol ding chule nalolhin tei ding ahi,” ati. Hichun David jong ajotna ding langa akichen, Saul jong akho lama ahung kile kit tan ahi.
\c 27
\s1 Philistine Te Lah’a David
\p 
\v 1 Ahinlah David ama le ama akingaiton, “Nikhat leh Saul in tha tei ding eigot ahitai. Kabol thei pentah chu ahile Philistine gam'a jamdoh ing ting, Chutileh, Saul in Israel gamsunga eidal le le hi bei tante chuteng hichu kahoidoh na achaina hitante,” ati.
\v 2 Hichun David in a sepai mi jagup akipuijin, Gath lengpa Moach chapa Achish ajoptai. David le a sepaite, chule a insung mite, Gath mun'a Achish toh acheng khom tauve.
\v 3 David chu aji teni, Ahinoam Jezreel a kon, chule Abigail, Nabal inneipi meithai Carmel’a kon hotoh hungkhom ahiuve.
\v 4 Saul in adel jamle le theilou nadingin David Gath lengpa kom'ah ajamlut tai tithu chu Saul in gangtah in ana jatan ahi.
\v 5 Nikhat David in Achish kom'ah, “Kachunga nalung alhaiya, nalungsetna kachanthei dinga ahile, hiche kho lehn ho lah a hin kachenna thei ding mun khat neipen, ajeh chu ipi dinga nasohpa hi hiche lengpa khopi sunga nang toh kachen khom khom thei ding ham?” ati.
\v 6 Hijeh chun Achish in hiche nikho chun Ziklag khopi chu David anape tai, hijeh a chu tuni chan geija Ziklag khopi hi Juda lengte chang den ahitai.
\v 7 Chule amaho Philistine mite lah a kum khat le lha li ana chenguve.
\v 8 David le a sepai te ana kon touvun Geshur mite le Girzi mite chule Amalek mite aga chom uvin ahi. Hiche mite ho hi Shur toh kinai, Egypt mite gamsunga ana chenglui ahi tauve.
\v 9 David in ana nokhum chun koimacha ana hinghoi pon ahi. Aman kelngoi, kelcha, bong, sangan, sa-ngong sao ana kikaiyin, chule ponho analan, Achish lengpa kom ana lhut in ahi.
\v 10 Achish in, “Tuchung koipen naga chom hitam?” tin anadongin ahile David in, “Juda gam lhanglam sang, Jerahmeel gamsung, Ken mite chenna gamsung dung pou kaga chom ahi,” ati.
\v 11 David chun koimacha numei pasal khen beiyin ana thatgam jin, ama le amite natoh dol chu Gath khoa gaseidoh ding aumjipoi. Philistine miho lah a aum sunga, avel vella hiche hi abol jing kei ahi.
\v 12 Achish chun David chu atahsan jeh chun, “Tuvang hin Israel miten David hi hatah in doudal tauvin tin, kakom'a uma a imatih chana kakin abol ding hita hi,” tin ana gel’e.
\c 28
\s1 Saul’in Gaochangnu Phun Asansah
\p 
\v 1 Phat chomkhat jouvin, Philistine miten gamsunga a sepai jouse akikhom un, Israel mite toh kisat dingin akigo tauve. Achish lengpan David jah ah, “Nangle na sepaiten galsat na-a neipan khompi diu ginchat aum'e,” ati.
\v 2 David jong nom in, “Aphalheh jenge! Ichan kabol the idol natahsa tah a namu ding ahi,” ati. Chuti chun Achish in David jah-a, “Keiman keima hinkho eivengtup dia kasem ding nahi,” ati.
\v 3 \x + \xo 28:3 \xt Thempu Dan 20:27; Danbu Ni Na 18:10,11\x*Samuel athi phat in, Israel pumpin alhaset piuvin, along a-op uvin, ama akhopi sung ma ma Ramah ah avuitauvin ahi. Chule Saul in agamsunga gaochang jouse le phunsan ho athisa ho lhagao ho toh kihoutoh ho jouse anomang tan ahi. \x + \xo 28:3 \xt 1 Samuel 25:1\x*
\v 4 Philistine te akikou khom’un, Shunem ah ngahmun asauvin chule Saul in Israel sepai jouse akhomin Gilboa ah ngahmun asemin ahi.
\v 5 Saul in Philistine sepai tamtah amu phat in akicha behseh jengin alungthim alinglao lheh jengtan ahi.
\v 6 Hichun aman, ipi kabolding hitam tin Pakai adongin, ahinlah Pakaiyin adonbut tapoi, mang hihenlang, chule Urim le Thummim phunsan jong chule themgao hijongleh iman adonbut tapoi. \x + \xo 28:6 \xt Minbu 27:21\x*
\v 7 Chuin Saul in athumop a pang ho asol’in, “Cheuvin lang Gaochang numei nei gahol peh un, keima chengting ama nu chu kagadoh ding ahi,” ati. Hiti chun athumop a pang ho khat in, “Endor mun ah Gaochang numei khat aum'e,” ahin atipeh in ahi.
\v 8 Hichun Saul in athempu von chol akhellin von mai mai in akivon in, jan in sepai mini akipuijin numeinu in'a chun acheuvin ahi. Chun aman, “Keiman athisa mi khat kakihoupi nome, a lhagao neikou peh thei dem?” ati.
\v 9 Numeinu chun, “Nangman tha ding a neigot ham? Saul in gamsunga konna gaochang jouse le phunsan them jouse adelmang hi nahet ding ahi. Chutia ahileh nangman ipi dinga keima kipalsahtei ding neigot ham?” ati.
\v 10 Ahinlah Saul chu Pakai min pan in akihah sellin akitem in ahi. “Tahbeh a hingjing Pakai min'a kasei ahi, hiche nabol jeh hin ima thilse umponte,” ati.
\v 11 Achainan numeinun jong, “Aphai, koipentah lhagao kakoudoh peh ding ham?” atile Saul in, “Samuel lhagao neikoudoh peh in,” ati.
\v 12 Numeinun Samuel amu phat in, ahung pengjah jengin, “Nangman neijou lhep’e, nangma Saul nahi!” ati.
\v 13 Hichun Lengpan amanu kom'ah, “Kicha hih in, koi namum?” atile amanun jong, “Pathen khat kamun leisetna kon'in ahung potdoh’e,” ahin ti.
\v 14 Saul in, “Amapa chu koitoh kilou’em? Ama chu tehsepu ahin, sangkhol chol khat aki’ah e,” ati. Saul in Samuel ahi ahechentan, chuin amasanga tol’ah abohkhup’in chibai abohtai.
\v 15 Hichun Samuel in, “Ipi jeh a neisuh boiya, neinung kou ham?” Chuin Saul in, “Ajeh chu keima kaboina asanglhehtai, Philistine ten galsat din ahung kigo uvin, Pathen'in eidalhatan, themgao ahilou le mang in jong eihetsah tapoi. Hijeh a chu nang kahin doh ahi, Ipi katiding hitam?” ati.
\v 16 Ahinla Samuel in adonbut in, “Pathen'in nadalhah tah’a, chule agalmi nahitah’a ahile, Ibola kei neidoh ham?” ati.
\v 17 “Pathenyin asei banga abol ahitai. Nalengam nanga konna alhe lhah a chule David joh apeh ahitai. \x + \xo 28:17 \xt 1 Samuel 15:28\x*
\v 18 Pakai thupeh jouse napalkeh’a, alungnat na naboldoh a, Amalek mite le anei jouseu na suhmang hel lou jeh a tua hi Pakaiyin hita abol ahitai. \x + \xo 28:18 \xt 1 Samuel 15:3-9\x*
\v 19 Chule jing nikho tengleh nang le na sepai te ho jouse Philistine te khut’a apeh doh ding ahitai, chule nangma le nachapa kaheng’a hung ding nahi lhon tai. Israel sepaite jong Pakaiyin Philistine te khut’a pedohtante,” ati
\v 20 Samuel thucheng seiho atijat behseh jeng jeh in, Saul chu tol’ah akijam jangden jengin ahi. Sun le jan’a an nelouva aum jeh in, agilkel in alhalhop jeng tan ahi.
\v 21 Numeinu chea agavet le, atijat val chu amudoh in, “Kapu, neilungset’in kenbon kahinkho phalngam’a neidoh ho kanop’a kabolpeh ngam le,
\v 22 Tun nangman jong kasei bangin bollin, neh ding phabep kapeh ding nahin, nenlang natha kidodoh sah kit in,” ati.
\v 23 Ahinlah Saul in ima neh ding anom pon, Chule avaipote ho geiyin nehsah tei ding agouvin, akhon khon nan anomin tol’a kon'in ahung kithoudoh in jalkhun chung’a atousah tauvin ahi.
\v 24 Hiche numeinu hin aina bongnou thaochet khat anei ahin, hichu agathat loiyin, changbong toh ameh nangjet in, cholsolouvin changlhah akangtan ahi.
\v 25 Chuin changlhah le bongsa chu Saul le aloi teni chu athuh peh in ahile ama hon anetauve. Aneh jou phat un hcihe jan chun amaho ahung kile kit tauve.
\c 29
\s1 Philistine Ten David Apaidoh’u
\p 
\v 1 Muntin'a Philistine sepaiho Aphek a akikhom khom’un, chule Israel te sepai chu Jezreel twinah phung mun’ah akikhom uve.
\v 2 Philistine lamkaihon, asepai te ho loi jakhat loi, loi sangkhat khat in akhen un alamkaiyun, David chule a sepai te ho Achish lengpa kom langa akijot un ahi.
\v 3 Ahinlah Philistine gal lamkaihon, “Hebrew mite ho hin hiche’a hi ipibolla hiuvem?” atiuve. Chuin Achish in, “Hiche pa hi David, Israel mite lengpa Saul sohpa chu ahi. Ama hi akum kum’a keitoh umkhom kahi lhonin, ahunglhun nia kipat, tuni chengeiyin athepmona imacha kamupoi,” ati.
\v 4 Ahinla Philistine lamkaiho chu alunghang un, “Nakhopi pehna a chun nungsol tan! Ama keihotoh galsat in konkhom thei pouvinte, ama galsatna mun’ah kilehei henlang Philistine mite eihin le sat kit u henlang, eiho luchang hijatpi hi kipoh henlang apupa toh kicham kit taleh, hiche tilouva aman thilpha abolthei ding adang ipi uma nangaitom?” atiuvin ahi.
\v 5 “Hiche David kitipa hi hilou ham? Mihon la abol uva, ‘Saul in mi asang asang athat in, David in mi sangsom som in athat’e, tia kisei chu? \x + \xo 29:5 \xt 1 Samuel 18:7; 21:11\x*
\v 6 Hichun Achish lengpan achaina in akouvin David jah ah, “Pakai hingjing min'a kasei ahi, nangma keidin nakitah lheh jengin ahi. Keima gellin nang toh galla ikon khom dingham kanati ahin, ajeh chu nahunglhun tilla kipat in tuni chan geijin nasuhkhel na imacha kamupon ahi. Ahivanginla Philistine lamkai len dang ho nangma toh gal isat khom diu hi, anom pouvin ahi.
\v 7 Lungset tah in achung uva lungnom mo louvin, lungmong in inlama kile kit tan,” ati.
\v 8 Hichun David in, “Ipi kanabol khella hitobang thilsoh ham? Nasohpa keima chunga hi ipi lung lhai louna na mudoh’a ka pakai le ka lengpa toh, galmi ho kasat khom thei lou hitam?” ati.
\v 9 Ahinlah Achish in, “Keima tah mudol in, nangma hi Pakai vantil bangin nadih lheh jenge, ahinlah Philistine gal lamkai hon gal nasat khompi ding akichauvin ahi.
\v 10 Hijeh chun, jingkah matah tengleh kithou vinlang namite ho jouse toh neidalha tauvin,” ati.
\v 11 Hiti chun David le aloite ho akigong’un, Philistine gamsung adalha tauvin ahi. Hiche phat chun Philistine sepai hon Jezreel ajon tauvin ahi.
\c 30
\s1 David In Amalek Mite Asuhmang
\p 
\v 1 Nithum jouvin, David le aloite ain’u Ziklag khopi agalhun phatun, Amalek miten Negev chule Ziklag ana sat uva, Ziklag khopi chu meiya ana hal vam’u agatoh khauvin ahi.
\v 2 Mihem khatcha that louvin, numeile chapang gei geiyin ana kaimang uvin ahi.
\v 3 Chuin David le amihon thilsoh le akisuh chimit chu amuva chule insung uva thil anasoh ho amu phat uvin,
\v 4 Amaho ha kan akap’un, acholdeh chan geiyin akap un ahi.
\v 5 David jiteni, Jezreela a konna Ahinoam chule Carmel a konna Nabal meithai, Abigail, teni jong chu akaimang nalah uva chu jaotha’ah ahi. \x + \xo 30:5 \xt 1 Samuel 25:42,43\x*
\v 6 Hijeh chun, David jong alung himo behseh jengtan ahi, ajeh chu amite ho jile chate ho jong ana kaimang u ahi. Ahinlah David in Pathen a kon'in thahatna akimu ben ahi.
\v 7 Hijeh chun Abiathar in thempupa jah a, “Thempu von ompho chu neihin hoipeh in,” ati. Hijeh chun Abiathar in hichu ahinchoi peh’in ahi \x + \xo 30:7 \xt 1 Samuel 22:20-23\x*
\v 8 Chuin David in jong Pakai adongin, “Hiche Amalek mite hi anung’u del leng kaphah ding hinam?” atileh Pakaiyin ahin adonbut in, “Henge, dellin, akaimangsa jouse jong nanung mu kit ding ahi!” ati.
\v 9 Hijeh chun David in mi jagup akigot in, Besor vadung ahungpha tauve.
\v 10 Sepaite jani vang chu Besor vadung agalkai ding’u chu alel behseh jeh’u chun, David chun amoh cheng mi jali toh adeltou peh uvin ahi.
\v 11 Ache uva ahile gamlah ah Egypt mite khat amandoh uvin David henga ahin akailut tauve. Ama hon neh ding changlhah phabep chule adonding twi apeuvin ahi.
\v 12 Chule theichang-ga a kisem changlhah lhon jong apeuvin aneh a adon jou phat in atha ahung hat dohtan ahi. Ajeh chu an nelou twidon louva nithum le janthum jen kelthoh a um anahitai.
\v 13 Chuin David in, “Hoiya hungkon nahia, koimi nahim” tia adoh le, “Keima Egypt mi gollhang kahin, Amalek mikhat soh kahi, nithum masanga pat’a chu damlou kahi, kadammo a kipat’a ka pakaipan eidalhah ahitai.
\v 14 Judah gamsung a Chereth mite gamsung’a Negev khopi, Caleb phung mite gamsung kachom un, chule Ziklag khopi chu meiyin kahal lhah uva hung kile kahiuve,” ati.
\v 15 Hichun David in, “Hiche michom ho kom'a chu neipuilut thei ding ham?” tia adoh le, gollhangpan, “Keima neitha da-a, chule kapu henga neipehdoh kit louding’a, Pathen min’a nakihahsel le, keiman napui nange,” ati.
\v 16 Hijeh chun David chu apuijin ahile ama hon Amalek mite ho chun Philistine gamsung le Judah gamsung’a konna achomdoh thilkeo simsen lou kipapina’a golnop abol uva, muntin'a akithe thang uva, ane pet u, adon pet u chule ala pet u, atohkha tauvin ahi.
\v 17 Chuti chun David le amiten anokhum un, jan khovah keiyin Amalek mite chu athat un ajing nilhum keiyin nilhangkai chan geiyin athat jingun ahi. Gollhang mi jali sangong sang chunga tou’a ajamdoh ho tilou adangse vang athat soh hel in ahi.
\v 18 Amalek miten alahpeh jouseu chu David in abonchan ainneipi teni jaonan anung lahpeh kittai.
\v 19 Imacha jong amangthah den aumpoi, aneo alen, chapa ahilou le chanu, abonchan akinung mu kittai.
\v 20 David chun kelngoi hon le bonghon jouse jong abonchan anung lahpeh kit in, amiten ahin hoilut soh tauve. Hichun ama hon, “Hiche hi David in gal’a achom doh ho ahi,” atiuve.
\v 21 Chuin David chu chol behseh jeh a Besor vadunga kidalha sepai jani heng’a achen, David le aloi adang ho amu phat uvin ahung potdoh uvin, kipah le thanom tah in ahung lamtouvin ahi.
\v 22 Ahin David mite lah miphalou boina sem jeng mi phabep khat ho chun, “Hiche eihotoh kilhonkhom lou ho hin hiche thilkeo kichomdoh ho hi kilah thei pouvinte,” ahin tiuve.
\v 23 Ahinlah David in, “Ahipoi, kasopi te ho, hiche thilkeo chunga hin kilosepou hite. Aman damsella eiven uva, galte eijosah uva, ijakaija eikithopiuva,
\v 24 Eihon hitia hi thu isei uleh kon nasei angai ding ham? Galkonpa chan jat chu thil ngahpa jong chang tei ding ahi,” tin ahin donbut in ahi.
\v 25 Hiche nia kipan chun David in chonna dan ding ana sem in, tuni geiyin Israel sunga chonna dan in akimangtai.
\v 26 Ziklag ahunglhun phat in, gal’a kihom doh thilkeo phabep chu aloi agol Judaho athot in hitin aseiye, “Hiche thilpeh hi nangho ding ahi, Pakai dougal te ho a kon ahi,” ati.
\v 27 Athilkeo athot ho chu anoiya khomite ding hi ahi, Bethel, Ramoth-negev, Jattir,
\v 28 Aroer, Siphmoth, Eshtermoa,
\v 29 Jerah’meel khopi Racal, Ken mite khopi dung’a chengte,
\v 30 Hormah, Bor-ashan, Athach,
\v 31 Hebron chujongleh David le asepaite toh akilon na muntin na athotsohkei uvin ahi.
\c 31
\s1 Saul Le Achapa Thi
\p 
\v 1 Philistine miten Israel mite chu anokhum tauvin ahile, Israel mite chu Philistine te masanga ajamcheh uvin, Gilboa molsanga ken laiyah chun Philistine ten athatgam tauve.
\v 2 Philistine miten Saul le achapa te ho jong adelphapa uvin, achapa thum Jonathan, Abinadab, chule Malkishua jong athat tauve.
\v 3 Saul panmun kimvel’a jong gal akihasat lheh jengun, akhona in thalpi kapthem hon akap kha’un, melsetah in amavo uvin ahi.
\v 4 Chuin Saul in agalvon popa jah ah, “Na chemjam satdoh inlang neithat in hiche Philistine Pathen helou ho ahung uva eimoh sutlih sang un,” ati. Ahinla agalvonpopa akichan athat ngampon ahi. Chuin Saul in jong ama chemjam asatdoh in, achemjam chu abokhum in ama le ama akithat tai.
\v 5 Chuin agalvon popan Saul athitai ti ahetdoh phat in achemjam asatdoh in alhuh khum in alengpa kom'ah ama jong athi tan ahi.
\v 6 Hiti chun Saul, achapa thumho, chule agalvon popa, abonchauvin nikhat sung in athi soh hel tauvin ahi.
\v 7 Jezreel phaicham agal langkhat, Jordan vadung niso lam’a Israel ten, Israel sepaite ho galjam gam tauve tithu ajahdoh uva, Saul le achapa te ho jong athat taove ti ajah phat un, akhopi hou adalhauvin ahile Philistine miten akhopi sung uva alut un khopi u chu alo tauvin ahi.
\v 8 Ajing nikho in Philistine miten mithilong ho hetup dinga ahung uleh Gilboa mol chunga Saul le achapa te thumho le agalvon popa, alongu ahung mudoh un ahi.
\v 9 Chuin Saul alu atan uvin agalvon chengtoh apotauve, Saul thi jeh in Philistine gamsung jouse le a pathen hounau Hou-In’ah kipa thuphon aneiyun ahi.
\v 10 Saul galvon chu amilim doi ahounao Ashteroth kiti Hou-In sung ah akoijun chule atahsa chu Beth-shan kiti khopi sunga bang ah akhaiyun ahi.
\v 11 Ahinlah Jabesh-gilead miten jong, Philistine miten Saul abolnao ajah phat un,
\v 12 Galhang pasal jouse akipat doh un, ahung kitol’un, jan khovah hellin Beth-shan a kon'in Saul le achapa te ho long chu banga kon'in ala lhauvin, Jabesh khopi ah ahin pulut un hikom'a chun ahalvam un ahi.
\v 13 Chujouvin agu ho chu alauvin Jabesh khoa Tamarisk thingphung noiyah avui uivn, chule nisagi jen apuldou nan an angol uvin ahi. 
